tion%20has%20visited%20relief%20camps%20at%20Churachandpur%2C%20Moirang%2C%20and%20Imphal%2C%20and%20interacted%20with%20the%20victims%2Finmates%20in%20the%20relief%20camps%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20silence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20shows%20%26quot%3Bhis%20brazen%20indifference%20to%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memorandum%20read%2C%20citing%20figures%20of%20the%20destruction%20in%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20that%20has%20continued%20for%20over%20three%20months%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20failure%20of%20both%20the%20Central%20and%20state%20government%20to%20protect%20the%20lives%20and%20properties%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20is%20apparent%20from%20the%20figures%20of%20more%20than%20140%20deaths%2C%20more%20than%20500%20injuries%2C%20burning%20of%20more%20than%205%2C000%20houses%20and%20internal%20displacement%20of%20more%20than%2060%2C000%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20incessant%20firing%20and%20arson%20of%20houses%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20establishes%2C%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20doubt%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20the%20state%20machineries%20have%20completely%20failed%20to%20control%20the%20situation%20for%20the%20last%20almost%20three%20months%2C%20the%20Opposition's%20memorandum%20to%20the%20Governor%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20condition%20in%20the%20relief%20camps%20%26quot%3Bis%20pathetic%20is%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20special%20care%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20children%20on%20a%20priority%20basis.%20The%20delegation%20argued%20that%20the%20continued%20internet%20ban%20for%20the%20last%20three%20months%20is%20aiding%20the%20unsubstantiated%20rumours%2C%20which%20is%20adding%20to%20the%20existing%20mistrust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sushmita%20Dev%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20assured%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20that%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20stands%20with%20them%20and%20will%20fight%20till%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20Parliament's%20monsoon%20session%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20accountable%26quot%3B%20to%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComing%20from%20the%20northeastern%20states%2C%20one%20has%20the%20feeling%20that%20people%20will%20forget%20us%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20accuse%20the%20opposition%20of%20doing%20photo-op%2C%20disrupting%20the%20Parliament%2C%20and%20not%20wanting%20to%20debate%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%20the%20Governor%20herself%20expressed%20her%20sorrow%20in%20the%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20also%20advised%20that%20we%20all%20speaking%20to%20all%20the%20leaders%2C%20be%20it%20Kuki%20or%20Meitei%2C%20of%20all%20communities%20and%20find%20a%20path%20to%20a%20solution.%20She%20also%20advised%20that%20an%20all%20party%20delegation%20should%20come%20to%20Manipur%20and%20speak%20to%20leaders%20of%20all%20communities%20because%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20mistrust%20that%20has%20been%20created%20among%20the%20people%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%20by%20everyone%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushmita%20Dev%20had%20earlier%20told%20PTI%20that%20among%20those%20they%20met%20was%20one%20of%20the%20two%20women%20who%20was%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%204%2C%20and%20her%20mother.%20The%20latter%20had%20one%20request%20for%20them%2C%20Ms%20Dev%20said%2C%20to%20help%20her%20at%20least%20see%20the%20bodies%20of%20her%20son%20and%20husband%2C%20who%20were%20killed%20during%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20slammed%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20and%20pointed%20to%20the%20alleged%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20optics.%20When%20this%20I.N.D.I.A.%20returns%20from%20Manipur%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20if%20he%20supports%20the%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20his%20state%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20Will%20these%2020%20MPs%20of%20I.N.D.I.A.%20(front)%20give%20reports%20on%20Rajasthan%20and%20West%20Bengal%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20asked%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20thus%20far%20refused%20to%20give%20in%20to%20demands%20of%20resignation%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20convene%20an%20assembly%20session%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%20or%20early%20August.%20At%20least%20180%20people%20have%20died%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690701420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fu6rau9k8_opposition-in-manipur_625x300_30_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-opposition-leaders-manipur-visit-complete-breakdown-opposition-delegation-in-appeal-to-manipur-governor-4252707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2021-member%20multi-party%20delegation%20of%20MPs%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20alliance%20that%20is%20in%20Manipur%20for%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20state%20today%20met%20Manipur's%20Governor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-opposition-leaders-manipur-visit-complete-breakdown-opposition-delegation-in-appeal-to-manipur-governor-4252707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-opposition-leaders-manipur-visit-complete-breakdown-opposition-delegation-in-appeal-to-manipur-governo