2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Chinese%20Aid'%3A%20Army%20Ex-Chief%20Gen.%20Naravane%20Says%20Foreign%20Interference%20in%20Manipur%20'Definitely%20There'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30122408%2FScreenshot-2023-07-30-at-11.28.2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Indian%20Army%20chief%2C%20retired%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%20has%20said%20that%20foreign%20interference%20in%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20and%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdefinitely%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20stressing%20that%20alleged%20Chinese%20aid%20to%20various%20insurgent%20groups%20has%20been%20continuing%20for%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnZLrw06Qy68%26ab_channel%3DIICProgrammes%5C%22%3E12th%20lecture%20of%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%20and%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20Conversations%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gen.%20Naravane%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20dangers%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-front%20war%2C%E2%80%9D%20heavily%20advocating%20for%20diplomacy%20to%20resolve%20conflicts%20for%20India%2C%20which%20faces%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-front%20threat%E2%80%9D%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20lecture%2C%20Gen.%20Naravane%20was%20asked%20by%20multiple%20journalists%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20and%20whether%20it%20amounted%20to%20a%20national%20security%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20on%20to%20Manipur%2C%20I%20had%20said%20right%20in%20the%20beginning%20that%20internal%20security%20is%20very%20important%20and%20if%20there%20is%20instability%20not%20only%20in%20our%20neighbouring%20country%20but%20in%20our%20border%20state%20then%20that%20instability%20is%20bad%20for%20overall%20national%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20retired%20general%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20decision%20makers%20on%20the%20gr