20of%20gross%20negligence%20and%20requests%20compensation%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20court%20documents%2C%20the%20attendants%20on%20a%209-hour%20flight%20from%20JFK%20Airport%20in%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Athens%2C%20Greece%20%26quot%3Bblatantly%20ignored%26quot%3B%20pleas%20for%20help%20from%20the%20plaintiffs%20and%20continued%20to%20serve%20the%20man%20drinks%20despite%20him%20being%20noticeably%20drunk%20and%20belligerent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Newyork%20claims%20that%20the%20drunk%20man%20behaved%20aggressively%20toward%20the%20plaintiffs%20and%20escalated%20into%20inappropriate%20touching%20over%20a%20nearly%20nine-hour%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20further%20claims%20that%20the%20staff%20allegedly%20permitted%20the%20drunken%20man%20to%20exit%20the%20plane%20at%20its%20destination%20without%20alerting%20local%20authorities%20or%20US%20law%20enforcement%20about%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%2C%20Fox%20Business%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intoxicated%20Delta%20passenger%20appeared%20to%20be%20getting%20drunker%20and%20drunker%20as%20the%20Delta%20flight%20attendants%20continued%20serving%20him%20alcohol%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20documents%20claim%20that%20the%20drunk%20passenger%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20a%20mother%20and%20a%20daughter.%20The%20man%20after%20a%20few%20drinks%20tried%20speaking%20to%20a%2016-year-old%20girl%2C%20who%20tried%20to%20ignore%20him.%20The%20man%20became%20aggressive%20toward%20the%20girl%20and%20began%20yelling%20at%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20made%20%26quot%3Bobscene%20gestures%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20her%20address%20and%20other%20information%20about%20her.%20The%20lawsuit%20claims%20that%20the%20man%20frightened%20her%20by%20putting%20his%20hands%20on%20her%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl's%20mother%20intervene