%20heat%20waves%20in%20February%20and%20March%2C%202023%2C%20causing%20the%20mustard%20to%20bloom%20at%20an%20unusual%20time.%20Then%2C%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20was%20hit%20with%20excessive%20hail%20storms%20and%20erratic%20rain.%20Temperatures%20in%20May%20became%20chilly%2C%20unexpectedly%2C%20while%20February%20and%20March%20were%20warm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20to%20get%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20this%20correspondent%20stopped%20in%20Pulwama%20and%20spoke%20with%20Javid%20Ahmed%20a%20high-density%20apple%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20over%20the%20world%20climate%20is%20changing.%20Uneven%20rains%2C%20meaning%20changing%20of%20conventional%20patterns%20and%20temperatures%20is%20badly%20affecting%20us%20too.%20February%20had%20May-June%20temperatures%20and%20there%20was%20cold%20wave%20in%20May.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20apple%20fruit%20size%20was%20affected%20and%20the%20fruits%20were%20not%20fully%20formed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F17184638%2Fpti-apples-kashmir.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22apples%20Kashmir%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F17184638%2Fpti-apples-kashmir.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F17184638%2Fpti-apples-kashmir-300x122.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F17184638%2Fpti-apples-kashmir-1024x416.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406060%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22488%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo%20of%20an%20apple%20market%20in%20Kashmir.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20worst%20affected%20are%20the%20upper%20Kashmir%20areas.%20I%20would%20estimate%2050%25%20losses%20in%20these%20regions%20and%20about%2020%25-30%25%20in%20lower%20regions%20like%20lower%20Anantnag.%20Hailstorms%20have%20also%20caused%20huge%20devastation%20in%20Pulwama%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJavid%20also%20showed%20us%20a%20%E2%80%9Chail%20net%E2%80%9D%20he%20has%20installed%20over%20his%20orchard%20to%20prevent%20damages.%20He%20believes%20without%20%E2%80%9Chail%20nets%E2%80%9D%20high%20density%20farming%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20with%20current%20weather%20patterns.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fclimate-chaos-in-kashmir-could-change-the-colour-of-our-kheer-and-a-whole-lot-more%5C%22%3EClimate%20Chaos%20in%20Kashmir%20Could%20Change%20the%20Colour%20of%20Our%20Kheer%2C%20and%20a%20Whole%20Lot%20More%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20tasting%20sour%20apples%20with%20Javid%20%3Cem%3Esaheb%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20correspondent%20spoke%20with%20Ghulam%20Muhamed%20Wani%20in%20Budgam.%20In%20his%20broken%20Hindi%20and%20Urdu%2C%20he%20explained%20that%20climate%20has%20been%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20the%20farmers.%20Wani%20saw%20it%20has%20divine%20rage.%20He%20had%2010%20%3Ci%3Ekanals%20%3C%2Fi%3Eof%20land%20and%20rented%20out%20another%2030%20kanals%20of%20plum%20orchards%2C%20right%20before%20the%20first%20hailstorms%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShowing%20us%20the%20damages%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20had%20two%20or%20three%20hailstorms%20till%20now%2C%20damaging%20most%20of%20the%20crops.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20May%20and%20then%2020%20days%20ago%2C%20we%20had%20experienced%20hailstorms.%20Our%20A-grade%20plum%20has%20become%20B-grade.%20And%20whereas%20I%20usually%20get%203%2C000%20boxes%20from%20my%2010%20kanals%2C%20this%20year%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20got%20800.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECherry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20talk%20about%20cherry%2C%20and%20this%20correspondent%20spoke%20with%20Tanveer%20Ul-Haq%20who%20works%20in%20the%20cherry%20canning%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20two%20varieties%20of%20cherry%20%E2%80%93%20early%20and%20mid%20varieties%20do%20well.%20But%20the%20late%20variety%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emishri%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20the%20most%20delicious%20and%20highest%20price%20fetching%20for%20farmers%20suffer%20under%20erratic%20rainfall%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Shopian%20region.%20Some%20farmers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20harvest%20the%20fruits%20because%20they%20were%20so%20damaged%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20from%20the%20production%20to%20the%20storage%20side%20of%20things%2C%20we%20met%20up%20with%20Maajid%20Wafai%2C%20president%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20fruit%20and%20vegetable%20processing%20and%20integrated%20cold%20chain%20association%2C%20JKPICCA.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%20Kashmir%20saw%20a%20bumper%20apple%20harvest.%20But%20excessive%20supply%20in%20the%20market%20resulted%20in%20a%20price%20crash%2C%20creating%20panic%20in%20the%20market.%20The%20input%20costs%20increased%20and%20revenue%20were%20halved.%20Overall%20a%20bad%20year%20for%20growers%20as%20transportation%20cost%20was%20huge%2C%20and%20input%20costs%20coupled%20by%20hails%20soured%20the%20harvests.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EOur%20A-grade%20apples%20became%20B-grade%20due%20to%20climate%20damages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20present%20situation%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20take%202021%20production%20figures%20as%20reference%20point%20for%20apple%20production.%20And%20we%20can%20comfortably%20assert%20that%20this%20year%20instead%20of%20the%20average%20of%202.2%20million%20tonnes%2C%20we%20have%20only%20about%201.5%20to%201.6%20million%20tonnes.%20The%20causes%20are%20clear%20and%20we%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20ruthless%20hailstorms%20and%20climate%20change.%20Customers%20will%20have%20to%20bear%2030-40%25%20increase%20in%20apple%20prices%20this%20year%20because%20it.%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20an%20environmentally%20fragile%20place.%20Our%20government%20should%20focus%20fully%20on%20saving%20of%20the%20environment%20of%20Kashmir.%20If%20this%20place%20is%20destroyed%20South%20Asia%20will%20suffer%20because%20all%20rivers%20comes%20from%20here.%20Agriculture%20is%20related%20to%20environment%20and%20we%20are%20witnessing%20an%20environmental%20catastrophe%20right%20now%2C%3Cspan%3E%20t%3C%2Fspan%3Ehe%20glaciers%20over%20Sonmarg%20area%20are%20not%20here%20for%20much%20longer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeasures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20word%2C%20we%20spoke%20with%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20horticulture%20department%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Shafiqa%20Khalid.%20In%20conversation%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20climate%20had%20changed%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CErratic%20rainfall%20and%20weather%20disturbances%20are%20signs%20of%20global%20warming.%20Every%20place%20in%20the%20world%20is%20experiencing%20this.%20We%20did%20have%20early%20blooming%20due%20to%20high%20heat%20situations.%20Weather%20typical%20to%20May%20and%20June%20was%20setting%20in%20in%20February%2C%20whereas%20May%20saw%20sudden%20rain%20and%20chilly%20weather%2C%20impacting%20various%20fruits.%20Pollution%20and%20other%20reason%20are%20responsible%20for%20these%20changes%2C%20directly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khalid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20nevertheless%2C%20our%20department%20is%20giving%20out%20advisories%20on%20hail%20and%20rainfall%20alerts.%20We%20are%20working%20with%20the%20farmers%20and%20also%20providing%20hail%20nets.%20The%20government%20has%20given%20a%20subsidy%20for%20putting%20up%20hail%20nets%20and%20we%20are%20doing%20our%20best.%20We%20even%20advise%20farmers%20on%20chemical%20use%20and%20fertilisers%20so%20they%20can%20recover%20from%20climate%20related%20damages%20and%20save%20their%20harvests%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20tweets%20at%20%40Indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690696667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30112321%2F14574895731_d12b7848dc_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fis-climate-change-already-affecting-kashmirs-fruit-crop%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cherry%2C%20apples%2C%20plum%20and%20strawberries%20%E2%80%93%20all%20fruit%20crop%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20under%20the%20weather%2C%C2%A0pushing%20traders%20and%20producers%20into%20panic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fis-climate-change-already-affecting-kashmirs-fruit-crop%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Yuvraj's%20six%20sixes%20sparked%20Broad's%20evolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690696565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102245548%2Cimgsize-44246.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fashes%2Fhow-yuvraj-singhs-six-sixes-sparked-stuart-broads-evolution-into-a-world-class-bowler%2Farticleshow%2F102245583.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20have%20been%20quite%20a%20few%20former%20Indian%20players%20who%20on%20record%20have%20said%20that%20Stuart%20Broad%20will%20always%20be%20remembered%20for%20the%20six%20sixes%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20in%20the%202007%20T20%20World%20Cup%20India-England%20clash%20at%20Durban.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A147%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22