%2Fmicron-s-global-suppliers-ready-plans-to-co-locate-ask-govt-help-123073000138_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmicron-s-global-suppliers-ready-plans-to-co-locate-ask-govt-help-123073000138_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Queen%20Barbie%20Vs%20King%20Oppenheimer%3A%20Both%20Offer%20Lessons%20in%20Gender%20Equality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI'm%20late%2C%20'cos%20I've%20been%20processing.%20Watching%20Margot%20Robbie%20and%20Ryan%20Gosling%20in%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Cillian%20Murphy%20and%20Robert%20Downey%20Jr%20in%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20almost%20back%20to%20back%20was%20an%20experience.%20It%20gave%20me%2C%20and%20I'm%20guessing%20a%20lot%20of%20us%2C%20a%20lot%20to%20process.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20most%20of%20us%20are%20not%20experts%2C%20not%20film%20critics%2C%20not%20fully%20sorted%20about%20feminism%20and%20patriarchy%2C%20not%20historians%2C%20we%20have%20little%20or%20no%20knowledge%20about%20quantum%20physics%20or%20splitting%20the%20atom%2C%20nor%20are%20most%20of%20us%20psychologists%20or%20sociologists.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20yet%2C%20we%20should%20have%20our%20say.%20After%20all%2C%20Greta%20Gerwig%20and%20Chris%20Nolan%20made%20these%20awesome%20movies%20for%20us.%20Also%2C%20it%20would%20be%20fully%20understandable%20if%20each%20of%20us%20walked%20away%20from%20these%20films%20with%20a%20take%20of%20our%20own.%20Here's%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20vs%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20More%20Alike%20Than%20You%20Might%20Think%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20even%20as%20the%20films%20are%20vastly%20different%20in%20every%20way%2C%20they%20are%20points%20at%20which%20they%20converge.%20Both%20have%20focused%20on%20some%20of%20biggest%20themes%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20focuses%20on%20the%20atom%20bomb%2C%20and%20through%20it%2C%20on%20the%20human%20ability%20to%20unleash%20horrific%20destruction%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20mankind's%20absurd%20movement%20towards%20developing%20the%20capacity%20of%20destroying%20itself.%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20talks%20about%20consumerism%2C%20and%20patriarchy%2C%20and%20the%20place%20of%20an%20iconic%20doll%20and%20the%20color%20pink%20in%20the%20understanding%20of%20feminism.%20But%20interestingly%2C%20these%20are%20some%20crucial%20overlaps%20in%20their%20themes%2C%20which%20we%20may%20have%20missed%20if%20the%20two%20films%20had%20not%20released%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnSince%20we%20find%20ourselves%20grappling%20and%20obsessing%20with%20them%20well%20into%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20its%20obvious%20that%20even%20at%20a%20societal%20level%2C%20these%20themes%20from%20the%20previous%20century%20are%20lot%20to%20process%2C%20and%20remain%20relevant%20today.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20with%20the%20subversive%20choice%20of%20Margot%20Robbie%20in%20the%20title%20role%2C%20sets%20up%20the%20Barbie%20doll%20phenomenon%20as%20something%20that%20inadvertently%20challenged%20patriarchy.%20It%20identified%20and%20blew%20up%20the%20massive%20purchasing%20power%20of%20the%20female%20consumer.%20And%20with%20all%20the%20other%20avatars%20of%20Barbie%2C%20from%20'President'%20Barbie%20to%20'Nobel%20Prize%20Winner'%20Barbie%2C%20it%20also%20created%20a%20sense%20of%20women%20succeeding%20as%20a%20gender%20in%2020th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETill%20Queen-dom%20Come%3A%20How%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20Subverts%20Toxic%20Masculinity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreta%20Gerwig%20then%20very%20cleverly%20busts%20this%20myth%2C%20by%20revealing%20that%20a%20Barbie-dom%20that's%20totally%20Barbie-driven%20and%20Barbie-centric%2C%20in%20which%20Ken%20and%20all%20Kens%20are%20secondary%2C%20is%20actually%20a%20gender-inverted%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20'real%20world'%2C%20which%20is%20totally%20male-centric%20and%20male-driven.%20The%20point%20is%20driven%20home%20further%20when%20Ken%2C%20played%20brilliantly%20by%20Ryan%20Gosling%2C%20stages%20a%20coup%2C%20dethrones%20Barbie%20and%20sets%20up%20a%20Ken-ruled%2C%20Ken-centric%2C%20Ken-dom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22arglvstg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Farglvstg_babrieembed_625x300_30_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E(A%20film%20still%20from%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20The%20'Ken-dom'%20Of%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20this%20tie%20in%20with%20'Oppenheimer'%3F%20Well%2C%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20Los%20Alamos%20was%20almost%20a%20Ken-dom.%20Almost%20every%20one%20of%20the%20atomic%20scientists%20and%20quantum%20physicists%20and%20mathematicians%20gathered%20there%20by%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%20was%20male.%20While%20there%20was%20the%20motivation%20of%20fighting%20fascism%2C%20fighting%20Nazi%20anti-semitism%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20boys'%20club.%20The%20race%20to%20split%20the%20atom%2C%20and%20the%20race%20to%20build%20the%20A-bomb%2C%20as%20shown%20by%20Nolan%2C%20also%20struck%20me%20as%20an%20all-male%2C%20narcissistic%20contest%2C%20in%20which%20the%20world-altering%20consequences%20of%20their%20actions%20were%20almost%20consciously%20ignored%2C%20so%20that%20they%20would%20simply%20not%20come%20in%20the%20way%2C%20until%20the%20'race'%20was%20won.%20At%20which%20point%2C%20as%20the%20film%20powerfully%20drives%20home%2C%20it%20is%20far%20too%20late.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnChristopher%20Nolan%20also%20chooses%20to%20give%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Oppenheimer's%20personal%20life%2C%20where%20again%20there%20is%20a%20hint%20of%20narcissism.%20His%20marriage%20to%20Kitty%20Puening%2C%20played%20in%20the%20film%20by%20Emily%20Blunt%2C%20had%20its%20controversy.%20He%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20her%20while%20she%20was%20married%2C%20which%20led%20to%20her%20divorce%2C%20after%20which%20she%20married%20Oppenheimer.%20We%20are%20also%20shown%20that%20Oppenheimer%20continued%20his%20on-off%20affair%20with%20Communist%20activist%20Jean%20Tatlock%2C%20even%20after%20his%20marriage%20to%20Kitty.%20Jean%20Tatlock%20suffered%20from%20depression%20and%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%201944.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20also%20see%20Cillian%20Murphy's%20Oppenheimer%20being%20given%20the%20option%20of%20choosing%20pacifism%20more%20than%20once%20before%20and%20during%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Manhattan%20Project%20that%20he%20headed%20in%20Los%20Alamos.%20But%20for%20the%20greater%20good%2C%20and%20perhaps%20for%20personal%20glory%2C%20he%20pressed%20on.%20And%20he%20ensured%20that%20his%20hand-picked%20all-star%20scientists'%20team%20stayed%20in%20line%20too%2C%20despite%20many%20of%20them%20questioning%20the%20motives%20of%20the%20project%2C%20and%20having%20several%20episodes%20of%20self-doubt.%20We%20see%20an%20Oppenheimer%20proud%20of%20winning%20the%20'atomic%20race'%2C%20applauding%20his%20team%20even%20after%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20were%20wiped%20out%2C%20and%20seemingly%20savouring%20his%20status%20as%20'father%20of%20the%20atomic%20bomb'%2C%20and%20seeing%20his%20face%20on%20the%20cover%20of%20TIME%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Destroyer%20Of%20Worlds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20the%20world%20then%20run%20and%20ruined%20by%20a%20boys'%20club%3F%20Is%20war%20a%20by-product%20of%20patriarchy%3F%20Was%20the%20nuclear%20weapons%20arms%20race%20and%20the%20cold%20war%20among%20the%20crudest%20examples%20of%20toxic%20masculinity%20taken%20to%20its%20extremes%3F%20There%20are%20many%20who%20would%20argue%2C%20yes.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20have%20always%20been%20other%20forces%20at%20play.%20Also%2C%20in%20the%20decades%20that%20have%20followed%2C%20we%20have%20had%20a%20few%20women%20leaders%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20have%20shown%20almost%20the%20same%20appetite%20for%20violence%20and%20destruction.%20So%2C%20no%20one%20is%20pedaling%20the%20old%20argument%20about%20how%20women%20'nurture'%2C%20while%20men%20'destroy'.%20That's%20too%20simplistic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%229u8oet6k%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F9u8oet6k_oppenheimerembed_625x300_30_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E(A%20film%20still%20from%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20can%20perhaps%20be%20said%2C%20is%20that%20both%20films%2C%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20key%20message%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20additional%20food%20for%20thought%2C%20remind%20us%20that%20gender%20equality%20is%20central%20to%20our%20lives%2C%20for%20us%20as%20individuals%2C%20and%20as%20a%20society.%20A%20'Barbie-dom'%20kind%20of%20world%20is%20not%20emancipating.%20It's%20a%20Xerox%20of%20patriarchy%2C%20but%20in%20reverse.%20And%20an%20'Oppenheimer-dom'%20lays%20bare%20the%20self-destructive%20endgame%20of%20a%20male-led%20world%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20a%20senseless%20contest%20of%20building%20atomic%20bombs%20and%20nuclear%20warheads%20that%20could%20destroy%20the%20world%20many%20times%20over.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhat%20this%20world%20needs%20to%20be%2C%20is%20neither%20Barbie's%20nor%20Oppenheimer's.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20genuinely%20respectful%20of%2C%20and%20driven%20by%2C%20every%20gender.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rohit%20Khanna%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20commentator%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20Managing%20Editor%20at%20The%20Quint%2C%20Executive%20Producer%20of%20Investigations%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Projects%20at%20CNN-IBN%2C%20and%20is%20a%202-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20award%20winner)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%2