0Gujjar%20leader%20from%20Rajouri%20district%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20was%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20a%20vote%20bank%E2%80%9D%20by%20%E2%80%9Cdestroying%20the%20identity%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20identity%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20tribals%20and%20it%20is%20being%20done%20in%20a%20manner%20similar%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20now%20Manipur.%20The%20tribal%20communities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20will%20not%20accept%20this%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Census%202011%2C%20there%20are%20between%20eight%20to%2012%20lakh%20Pahari-speaking%20people%2C%20and%20about%2015%20lakh%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakerwals%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20live%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20which%20comprises%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20districts%20of%20Jammu%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20groups%20can%20together%20influence%20the%20outcome%20of%20elections%20in%2025%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jammu-based%20editor%20and%20political%20analyst%20Zafar%20Chaudhary.%20The%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20brighten%20its%20prospects%20on%20these%20seats%20by%20wooing%20the%20Paharis%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Communities%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujjar-Bakerwal%20tribes%20and%20the%20Pahari%20community%20share%20a%20similar%20social%20and%20cultural%20milieu%20and%20together%20form%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region.%20The%20Gujjars%20mostly%20live%20a%20nomadic%20life%20by%20shuttling%20between%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20regions%20with%20their%20livestock%20of%20buffaloes%2C%20sheep%20and%20goats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Paharis%20are%20a%20socially%20stratified%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mostly%20financially%20well-off%20and%20culturally%20moored%20%E2%80%93%20community%20with%20caste%20and%20other%20ethnic%20divisions%2C%20who%20are%20joined%20by%20the%20thread%20of%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Union%20government%20read%20down%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20solid%20electoral%20footing%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20is%20attempting%20to%20make%20inroads%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20where%20it%20hopes%20to%20dent%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20traditional%20parties%20like%20National%20Conference%20and%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20by%20allegedly%20creating%20divisions%20within%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakerwals%2C%20and%20Paharis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2025%2C%202019%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20Paharis%20met%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20seeking%20ST%20status%20for%20the%20community.%20In%20January%202020%2C%20the%20Paharis%20were%20given%20a%204%25%20reservation%20in%20the%20OBC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEx-MLC%20Sh.%20%40BjpVibodh%2C%20led%20a%20delegation%20of%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Pahari%20Cultural%20and%20Welfare%20Forum%20meets%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Sh.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AmitShah%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Sh%20Ajit%20Doval%20(NSA)%20in%20New%20Delhi%20over%20granting%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20to%20'Pahari'%20speaking%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1n3qO8KXrW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1n3qO8KXrW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20BJP%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20(%40BJP4JnK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4JnK%2Fstatus%2F1210853550063898626%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2028%2C%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Commission%20on%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Classes%20headed%20by%20G.D.%20Sharma%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20government.%20In%20its%202022%20report%2C%20the%20commission%20recommended%20inclusion%20of%20Paharis%2C%20Paddari%2C%20Koli%20and%20Gadda%20Brahman%20communities%20as%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20supported%20the%20proposal%20following%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%2C%20the%20Gujjar%20leader%2C%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20ST%20reservation%20for%20Paharis%20was%20raised%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20political%20interests.%20Terming%20the%20move%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfraud%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20member%20from%20the%20tribal%20communities%20in%20the%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20so%20many%20years%2C%20the%20ST%20commission%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20Paharis%20as%20a%20tribal%20community%20but%20suddenly%20it%20has%20had%20a%20change%20of%20mind%20because%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power.%20The%20Sharma%20commission%20made%20political%20recommendations%20and%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20STs%20closed%20its%20eyes%20to%20this%20attack%20on%20the%20identity%20of%20tribals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98True%20empowerment%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%2C%20the%20ARCJAC%20founder-member%2C%20said%20that%20the%20law%20has%20set%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20criteria%E2%80%9D%20for%20granting%20tribal%20status%20to%20any%20minority%20community.%C2%A0%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20community%20has%20to%20be%20ethnically%20distinct%20or%20economically%20backward.%20Both%20these%20criteria%20don%E2%80%99t%20fit%20the%20Paharis.%20The%20Sharma%20commission%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20care%20to%20see%20that%20not%20even%20one%20criteria%20was%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20Paharis%20before%20making%20its%20recommendation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoudhary%20said%20that%20the%20Pahari%20community%20has%20different%20castes%20and%20if%20the%20Bill%20is%20passed%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20300%20more%20castes%20will%20be%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20tribals%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20presently%20includes%20only%20five%20tribes%20%E2%80%93%20Gujjars%2C%20Bakerwals%2C%20Shinas%2C%20Gaddis%20and%20Spitis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20Bukhari%20(caste%20name)%20of%20Poonch%20gets%20tribal%20status%2C%20how%20can%20the%20government%20deny%20it%20to%20a%20Bukhari%20in%20Srinagar%3F%20There%20is%20no%20criteria%20for%20defining%20who%20is%20Pahari%3F%20The%20whole%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20become%20a%20state%20of%20tribals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20BJP%20truly%20wants%20to%20empower%20the%20Paharis%2C%20they%20should%20be%20provided%20political%20reservation%20like%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20and%20refugees%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20been%20given%20recently.%20Giving%20them%20tribal%20status%20will%20shrink%20the%20opportunities%20which%20are%20aimed%20at%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20empowerment%20of%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakerwals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%2C%20and%20Paharis%2C%20have%20met%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20over%20the%20issue%20in%20recent%20weeks%20and%20months%20but%20the%20meetings%20have%20failed%20to%20end%20the%20deadlock.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20says%20that%20granting%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis%20will%20not%20affect%20the%20reservation%20benefits%20of%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20of%20quota%20within%20quota%20in%20the%20reservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hussain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Mass%20agitation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribals%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20are%20preparing%20for%20a%20mass%20agitation%20if%20the%20Union%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20roll%20back%20its%20decision.%20A%20major%20protest%20is%20being%20planned%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20August%20in%20Jammu.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Dalit%20leader%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20and%20tribal%20leaders%20of%20the%20country%20have%20extended%20their%20support%20to%20the%20agitation%20and%20a%20mahapanchayat%20is%20also%20being%20planned%20in%20Jammu%20in%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20is%20no%20more%20in%20our%20hands%20now%20because%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20concern%20the%20tribals%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20only.%20It%20will%20affect%20the%20tribals%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20last%20year%2C%20we%20have%20been%20coming%20out%20on%20the%20roads%20and%20staging%20peaceful%20protests.%20Now%20our%20livestock%20will%20join%20us%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20introduce%20the%20Bill%20for%20providing%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmehbooba-mufti-omar-abdullah-criticise-jk-admins-land-to-landless-plan%5C%22%3Eapproving%20a%20controversial%20%E2%80%98land%20for%20landless%E2%80%99%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20opposition%20has%20termed%20the%20scheme%20aimed%20at%20changing%20the%20demography%20of%20the%20Muslim-majority%20region%20by%20settling%20non-locals%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20woo%20the%20Hattee%20community%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20by%20granting%20them%20tribal%20status%20failed%20to%20yield%20any%20electoral%20dividends%20as%20it%20lost%20the%20assembly%20elections%20while%20the%20proposed%20move%20to%20declare%20Meiteis%20in%20Manipur%20as%20tribals%20has%20triggered%20large-scale%20protests%20acro