C%20reasoning%20and%20motor%20control%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20after%20the%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwellness%2F2023%2F07%2F26%2Flong-covid-brain-function-cognition-memory%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20researchers%20used%20an%20online%20platform%20to%20test%20thousands%20of%20people%20to%20understand%20how%20COVID%20has%20affected%20brain%20function%20and%20how%20long%20those%20symptoms%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENathan%20Cheetham%2C%20a%20senior%20postdoctoral%20data%20scientist%20at%20King's%20College%20London%20led%20the%20study%2C%20he%20revealed%20that%20it%20allowed%20them%20to%20quantify%20how%20big%20the%20effect%20of%20covid%20is%20and%20who%20was%20most%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20across%20the%20globe%20have%20reported%20symptoms%20of%20long%20covid.%20The%20media%20outlet%20reported%20that%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20millions%20of%20people%20suffered%20from%20the%20symptoms.%20The%20symptoms%20of%20long%20covid%20can%20include%20fatigue%2C%20respiratory%20and%20heart%20problems%2C%20digestive%20problems%20and%20neurological%20issues%20such%20as%20brain%20fog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neurological%20symptoms%20include%20brain%20fog%2C%20numbness%2C%20tingling%2C%20headache%2C%20dizziness%2C%20blurred%20vision%2C%20tinnitus%20and%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20S.%20Nordvig%2C%20a%20neurologist%20at%20Weill%20Cornell%20Medicine%20who%20founded%20a%20clinic%20for%20long-haulers%20with%20brain%20fog%20told%20Washington%20Post%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20some%20contention%20about%20whether%20the%20cognitive%20effects%20of%20an%20earlier%20covid%20infection%20do%20actually%20persist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Nordvig%20said%20that%20in%20her%20own%20practice%2C%20she%20has%20seen%20these%20symptoms%20persist%20-%20unfortunately%2C%20over%20three%20years%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20and%20many%20times%20after%20just%20a%20mild%20covid%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECognitive%20difficulties%20are%20the%20most%20common%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20long%20covid%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreg%20Vanichkachorn%2C%20medical%20director%20of%20the%20Covid%20Activity%20Rehabilitation%20Program%20at%20Mayo%20Clinic%20told%20the%20media%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20tend%20to%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20folks%20get%20better%20with%20physical%20things%20like%20their%20fatigue%20and%20their%20endurance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20cognitive%20deficits%2C%20those%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20seem%20to%20last%20the%20longest.%20Sometimes%20they%20never%20go%20away%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20had%20to%20permanently%20adapt%20in%20order%20to%20continue%20functioning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20researchers%20at%20King's%20College%20London%20observed%203%2C335%20voluntary%20participants%20by%20using%20an%20online%20platform.%20The%20research%20showed%20that%20participants%20who%20had%20been%20experiencing%20long-covid%20symptoms%20for%2012%20weeks%20or%20more%20were%20found%20to%20have%20significantly%20larger%20cognitive%20deficits%20-%20comparable%20to%20a%2010-year%20increase%20in%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690690980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fsehipu9o_dementia_625x300_20_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flong-covid-patients-continue-to-struggle-with-brain-function-for-at-least-two-years-study-4252465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20neurological%20symptoms%20include%20brain%20fog%2C%20numbness%2C%20tingling%2C%20headache%2C%20dizziness%2C%20blurred%20vision%2C%20tinnitus%20and%20fatigue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flong-covid-patients-continue-to-struggle-with-brain-function-for-at-least-two-years-study-4252465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-