t%20to%20Korean%20firms%20like%20LG%20and%20Samsung%2C%20which%20extended%20their%20use%20into%20mobile%20phones.%20Then%20came%20China.%20It%2C%20too%2C%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20cells%20through%20reverse%20engineering%20and%20joint%20ventures.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20lithium%20ion%E2%80%99s%20use%20cases%20expanded%20yet%20again%20%E2%80%93%20to%20now%20include%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20hinges%20the%20eventual%20question%20of%20how%20much%20demand%20there%20will%20be%20for%20critical%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20Beijing%20Olympics%2C%20China%20began%20subsidising%20EV%20buyers.%20In%20tandem%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchinas-ev-juggernaut-is-a-warning-for-the-west-1389f718%5C%22%3Eswitched%20public%20procurement%20of%20taxis%20and%20buses%20to%20EVs%20and%20got%20provincial%20governments%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3Eto%20stump%20up%20capital%20for%20lithium%20mining%20and%20refining%20for%20EV%20batteries%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Localisation%20also%20became%20a%20focus.%20To%20win%20subsidies%2C%20cars%20had%20to%20be%20locally%20made%2C%20with%20components%20manufactured%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20country%20is%20an%20EV%20powerhouse.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20control%20the%20raw%20materials%20needed%20for%20making%20electric%20vehicles%20but%20it%20also%20has%20expertise%20in%20processing%20and%20refining%20them%20as%20well%20as%20in%20manufacturing%20end-use%20applications%20such%20as%20batteries%20and%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20other%20countries%20are%20trying%20to%20reprise%20China%E2%80%99s%20success.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdigging-into-indias-dash-for-critical-minerals%5C%22%3Efirst%20part%20of%20this%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20spoke%20about%20the%20US%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act.%20Another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-u-s-wants-a-rare-earths-supply-chain-heres-why-it-wont-come-easily-dfc3b632%5C%22%3Eproposed%20bill%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20a%20%2420-a-kilogram%20credit%20for%20US-made%20magnets.%20Manufacturers%20sourcing%2090%25%20of%20their%20component%20parts%20from%20US%20producers%20could%20be%20entitled%20to%20a%20%2430-a-kilogram%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20too%2C%20has%20taken%20a%20similar%20approach.%20In%20the%20mobility%20sector%2C%20through%20schemes%20like%20FAME%2C%20it%20has%20subsidised%20EV%20buyers.%20The%20country%20is%20also%20pushing%20the%20use%20of%20electric%20buses%20in%20public%20transport.%20And%2C%20with%20the%20Production%20Linked%20Incentive%20Scheme%20(PLI)%20scheme%20for%20advanced%20chemical%20cell%20batteries%2C%20the%20country%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20an%20indigenous%20value%20chain%20for%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20an%20indigenous%20value%20chain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20%3Cem%3ECarbonCopy%3C%2Fem%3E%20asked%20Union%20government%20advisor%20Randheer%20Singh%20about%20these%20schemes.%20Till%20June%20this%20year%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20director%20(e-mobility)%20and%20senior%20team%20member%20(advanced%20chemistry%20cells%20programme)%20at%20Niti%20Aayog.%20He%20left%20NITI%20to%20start%20his%20own%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFAME%20is%20a%20demand%20incentive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20all%20countries%20have%20created%20such%20schemes%20to%20bring%20about%20behavioural%20changes.%E2%80%9D%20In%20tandem%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20country%20has%20rolled%20out%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20for%20batteries.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20companies%20will%20have%20to%20ensure%20localisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20they%20have%20to%20ensure%20a%20minimum%20of%2025%25%20localisation%20in%20their%20batteries.%20Five%20years%20after%20the%20award%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20localisation%20has%20to%20rise%20to%2060%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20use%20locally-made%20cells%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20will%20have%20either%20locally-made%20CAM%2C%20electrolyte%20or%20anode.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20PLI%2C%20the%20push%20is%20to%20start%20making%20cells%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Uttam%20Sen%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20e-TRNL%20Energy%2C%20a%20Bangalore-based%20startup%20trying%20to%20make%20cells%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20next%20push%20will%20be%20to%20make%20cathodes%2C%20anodes%20and%20electrolytes%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20not%20all.%20India%20is%20also%20seeing%20companies%20outside%20PLI%20invest%20in%20battery%20manufacturing.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20another%20lot%20coming%20up%20in%20ACC%20%5BAdvanced%20Chemistry%20Cells%5D%20without%20government%20incentive%20for%20cell%20manufacturing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20these%20companies%2C%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20localisation%20targets%20might%20not%20localise%20the%20critical%20components.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20them%20to%20localise%2C%20too%2C%20the%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiaesa.info%2Fnews-menu%2F1903-india-set-to-acquire-lithium-for-ev-batteries-in-6-months%5C%22%3Edoubled%20the%20basic%20import%20duty%20on%20lithium-ion%20cells%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2010%25.%20As%20for%20battery%20packs%20used%20in%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20the%20import%20duty%20has%20been%20tripled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20boost%20local%20manufacturing%20of%20solar%20panels.%20To%20reduce%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20reliance%20on%20China%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20boost%20local%20manufacturing%20of%20panels%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Findia-may-cut-solar-panel-import-tax-to-make-up-domestic-shortfall%2Farticleshow%2F100623665.cms%5C%22%3Estiff%20import%20duties%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20slapped%20on%20imported%20panels.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20created%20an%20outcome%20where%20developers%20said%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20RE%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20how%20is%20this%20approach%20working%20in%20the%20context%20of%20EVs%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20users%20of%20critical%20minerals%20like%20lithium%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20India%20source%20the%20technology%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20article%20was%20getting%20written%2C%20two%20announcements%20stunned%20EV%20sector%20watchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20at%20a%20time%20most%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20have%20an%20energy%20density%20below%20300%20watthours%2Fkilogram%2C%20CATL%20unveiled%20a%20battery%20that%20stores%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fscience%2F2023-05-03%2Fcatl-announces-battery-to-make-electric-aviation-possible%2F102289310%5C%22%3E500%20wh%2Fkg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20battery%2C%20it%20said%2C%20will%20be%20useful%20for%20electric%20flights%20as%20well%20as%20boost%20EVs%E2%80%99%20range%20to%201%2C000%20km%20per%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20even%20more%20staggering%20announcement%20followed%20in%20the%20subsequent%20weeks.%20This%20one%20was%20from%20Toyota%2C%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.motortrend.com%2Fnews%2Ftoyota-ev-strategy-sales-panic-electric-cars-akio-toyoda%2F%5C%22%3Eunder%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20delaying%20a%20switch%20to%20fully%20EV%20models.%20Early%20in%20July%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20it%20had%20developed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F87cb8e92-8e82-4755-8fc3-2943f8f63e1d%5C%22%3Esolid%20state%20battery%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20give%20EVs%20a%20range%20of%201%2C200km%20and%20a%20charging%20time%20of%2010%20minutes%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20India%20tries%20to%20create%20its%20own%20indigenous%20EV%20supply%20chain%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20starting%2