overnment%20approval%20for%20around%20two%20years%20to%20raise%20funds%20from%20its%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20little%20success%20so%20far%2C%20it%20has%20now%20started%20looking%20for%20other%20options%20to%20raise%20the%20required%20capital%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrote.%20BYD%2C%20too%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Findia-is-not-keen-on-allowing-chinese-ev-maker-byd-to-set-up-shop-amid-border-tensions-report%2Farticleshow%2F101773537.cms%5C%22%3Efacing%20similar%20hurdles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20MG%20Motor%20is%20also%20wondering%20if%20it%20should%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fauto-news%2Fril-in-fray-as-mg-motor-looks-to-sell-india-ops-reports%2Farticleshow%2F100149351.cms%5C%22%3Ehydrogen%20fuel%20cells%20and%20battery%20cells%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20such%20an%20arrangement%20is%20expected%20to%20work%20is%20clear%20enough.%20MG%20will%20source%20tech%20from%20its%20parent%20%E2%80%93%20and%20manufacture%20in%20India.%20Once%20such%20companies%20are%20compelled%20to%20make%20in%20India%2C%20the%20manufacturing%20know-how%20will%20spread%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20joint%20ventures%20are%20how%20China%2C%20too%2C%20has%20acquired%20manufacturing%20know-how.%20Given%20the%20large%20size%20of%20the%20Indian%20market%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20safe%20to%20assume%20that%20foreign%20makers%20will%20come.%20The%20country%20wants%20them%20to%20get%20their%20vendors%20along.%20As%20this%20article%20was%20being%20written%2C%20news%20came%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftesla-battery-supplier-panasonic-in-talks-to-set-up-plant-in-india-123071300669_1.html%5C%22%3ETesla%20has%20asked%20its%20battery%20suppliers%20to%20start%20talks%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20set%20up%20battery%