o%20buy%20from%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20agreed%20Sunkavalli.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20more%20scale.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20startups%20are%20looking%20overseas%20for%20growth.%20Take%20Epsilon.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fepsilon-advanced-materials-to-up-india-capacity-from-200-tpa-to-10-000-123070600968_1.html%5C%22%3Eanode%20maker%20is%20boosting%20its%20production%20capacity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20to%2010%2C000%20TPA.%20It%E2%80%99s%2C%20however%2C%20setting%20up%20a%2050%2C000%20TPA%20unit%20in%20the%20US%2C%20enough%20to%20power%20a%20million%20EVs.%20Or%20take%20the%20Tata%20Group.%20It%E2%80%99s%20setting%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pv-magazine-india.com%2F2023%2F06%2F05%2Ftata-group-to-set-up-20-gwh-lithium-ion-cell-plant-in-gujarat%2F%5C%22%3E20%20GWh%20lithium%20ion%20cell%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autocarindia.com%2Findustry%2Ftata-group-confirms-ev-battery-factory-in-the-uk-428795%5C%22%3E40%20GWh%20battery%20plant%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20also%20looking%20to%20export%20from%20India.%20%E2%80%9CCovid%20has%20taken%20its%20toll%20on%20China%E2%80%99s%20reputation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20promoter%20of%20an%20EV%20component%20maker%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20wants%20a%20supply%20chain%20shock.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20trade%20war%20is%20underway.%E2%80%9D%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCountries%20like%20Japan%20are%20under%20pressure%20to%20find%20cell%20manufacturers%20outside%20China.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20China%20Plus%20One%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20like%20BTR%20and%20Shanshan%20Energy%2C%20they%20make%20CAM%20for%20about%20%2420%2Fkilo%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varma%20had%20added.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20scale%20is%20very%20low%2C%20our%20cost%20will%20come%20to%20about%20%2424-25.%20That%20is%20a%20premium%20European%20and%20Far-East%20companies%20say%20they%20are%20very%20willing%20to%20pay%2C%20to%20secure%20alternate%20supply%20chains%20outside%20of%20China.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20delivering%20growth%2C%20this%20focus%20on%20export%20markets%20serves%20another%20end.%20%E2%80%9C(Firms)%20should%20go%20through%20this%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahul%20Walawalkar%2C%20the%20head%20of%20India%20Energy%20Storage%20Alliance.%20%E2%80%9CSelling%20in%20global%20markets%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20show%20that%20their%20product%20is%20competitive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bigger%20question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20how%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20atmanirbharta%20in%20critical%20minerals%20unfolding%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20series%20has%20shown%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20to%20give%20a%20categorical%20answer%20to%20that%20question.%20Too%20many%20pieces%20of%20this%20puzzle%20%E2%80%93%20geopolitics%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20source%20critical%20minerals%20supplies%2C%20local%20demand%20for%20end-use%20applications%20like%20battery%20components%E2%80%94are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20flux.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20recycling%2C%20domestic%20exploration%2C%20the%20mineral%20security%20partnership%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20outreach%20to%20countries%20like%20Australia%2C%20the%20country%20seems%20to%20have%20multiple%20pathways%20for%20securing%20its%20critical%20mineral%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20take%20a%20closer%20look%20and%20questions%20emerge.%20While%20working%20on%20this%20report%2C%20CarbonCopy%20was%20told%20by%20an%20industry%20observer%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20that%20many%20manufacturers%20do%20not%20want%20to%20stray%20beyond%20their%20core%20functions%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20engineering%20into%20the%20messy%20world%20of%20critical%20mineral%20mining.%20And%20so%2C%20will%20private%20companies%20want%20their%20own%20mines%20or%20will%20they%20be%20happier%20with%20an%20intermediary%20%E2%80%93%20KABIL%20or%20global%20traders%20like%20Glencore%20%E2%80%93%20supplying%20critical%20minerals%20to%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20questions.%20Does%20KABIL%20have%20the%20resources%20(staffing%2C%20budgets%20and%20diplomatic%20support)%20to%20compete%20with%20other%20countries%3F%20How%20is%20India%20placed%20vis-a-vis%20critical%20minerals%E2%80%99%20refining%20technologies%3F%20How%20will%20the%20Mineral%20Security%20Partnership%20work%20%E2%80%93%20and%20what%20will%20be%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20within%20that%3F%20What%20parts%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20chain%20will%20come%20to%20India%3F%20As%20the%20sole%20developing%20country%20in%20the%20partnership%E2%80%94one%20with%20lax%20environmental%20regulation%2C%20additionally%20%E2%80%93%20might%20India%20end%20up%20being%20the%20most%20polluting%20parts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20are%20the%20questions%20that%20surround%20demand.%20Can%20India%20create%20enough%20demand%20%E2%80%93%20across%20renewables%2C%20grid%20storage%2C%20EVs%20%E2%80%93%20to%20create%20an%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20sector%20that%20absorbs%20these%20critical%20minerals%3F%20Without%20that%2C%20firms%20will%20keep%20importing%20components%E2%80%94and%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20dependence%20on%20other%20nations%20will%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20how%20are%20the%20firms%20which%20won%20the%20PLI%20for%20rechargeable%20batteries%20faring%3F%20How%20fast%20will%20the%20market%20for%20EVs%20grow%3F%20Unlike%20steel%20which%2C%20threatened%20by%20measures%20like%20carbon%20border%20taxes%2C%20is%20going%20green%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20automotive%20cluster%20is%20still%20unsure%20how%20rapidly%20the%20domestic%20market%20will%20decarbonise.%20It%20wants%20to%20invest%20cautiously.%20Caution%2C%20however%2C%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20risks.%20As%20other%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20those%20with%20booming%20EV%20markets%20%E2%80%93%20invest%20in%20batteries%20and%20battery%20components%2C%20the%20minimum%20viable%20scale%20for%20plants%20is%20rising%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardwired%20into%20all%20this%20is%20also%20the%20question%20of%20technology.%20Will%20Indian%20units%20sourcing%20technology%20through%20joint%20ventures%20or%20developing%20it%20inhouse%20as%20scrappy%20startups%20be%20globally%20competitive%3F%20How%20will%20the%20entry%20of%20firms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Fbyd-seeks-nod-for-1-billion-plan-to-build-evs-batteries-in-india-reuters-reports-citing-sources%2Farticleshow%2F101750378.cms%5C%22%3EBYD%3C%2Fa%3E%20(even%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Findia-is-not-keen-on-allowing-chinese-ev-maker-byd-to-set-up-shop-amid-border-tensions-report%2Farticleshow%2F101773537.cms%5C%22%3Elocal%20JV%20partner%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20Tesla%20change%20this%20landscape%3F%20EVs%20might%20get%20a%20boost%20with%20these%20firms%E2%80%99%20entry%20but%20how%20much%20of%20their%20supply%20chain%20will%20they%20localise%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20critical%20minerals%20is%20no%20ordinary%20puzzle.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20puzzle%20with%20shape-shifting%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWait%20and%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarboncopy.info%2Fcan-india-create-an-atmanirbhar-ev-manufacturing-chain%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarboncopy.info%2F%5C%22%3ECarbonCopy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690684215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F17175040%2Fmichael-marais-HjV_hEECgcM-unsplash.jp