e%20faith%20that%20FLDOE%20will%20correct%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Donalds%20added%2C%20referencing%20the%20Florida%20Department%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Byron%20Donalds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c5378f048ff200190d979b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Byron%20Donalds%20of%20Florida.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20DeSantis%20got%20word%20of%20the%20remarks%2C%20he%20lashed%20out%20at%20Donalds%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20issue%20by%20reporters%20in%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20you%20got%20to%20choose%3A%20Are%20you%20going%20to%20side%20with%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20liberal%20media%20outlets%20or%20are%20you%20going%20to%20side%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Florida%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20very%20clear%20that%20these%20guys%20did%20a%20good%20job%20on%20those%20standards.%20It%20wasn't%20anything%20politically%20motivated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonalds%20on%20Friday%20made%20an%20appearance%20on%20Fox%20News%2C%20where%20he%20pointed%20to%20the%20DeSantis%20campaign%20over%20the%20dustup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20be%20clear.%20I%20don't%20even%20have%20a%20criticism%2C%26quot%3B%20Donalds%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20issue%20is%20with%20one%20sentence%20of%20the%20entire%20thing%2C%20one%20sentence%20of%20200%20pages.%20And%20the%20DeSantis%20team%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20big%20issue%20out%20of%20it%3F%20That's%20ridiculous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20been%20rising%20in%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20polls%20in%20recent%20weeks%20and%20could%20threaten%20DeSantis'%20current%20status%20as%20the%20most%20formidable%20alternative%20to%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20called%20out%20the%20governor%20o