t-trump-defamation-lawsuit-against-cnn%2Famp_articleshow%2F102237230.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Vice%20of%20Spice%3A%20Confronting%20Lead-Tainted%20Turmeric%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28174539%2FUndark-turmeric-lead-photo.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.undark.org%5C%22%3EUndark%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fundark.org%2F2023%2F07%2F19%2Fthe-vice-of-spice-confronting-lead-tainted-turmeric%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20heat%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20the%20day%20set%20in%2C%20dozens%20of%20people%20were%20already%20gathered%20under%20a%20large%20banyan%20tree%20at%20the%20twice-weekly%20turmeric%20market%20in%20Ataikula%2C%20Bangladesh.%20The%20season%20for%20harvesting%20turmeric%20was%20quickly%20coming%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20had%20arrived%20watched%20from%20the%20shade%20as%20other%20farmers%20brought%20their%20haul%20on%20motorbikes%20and%20auto%20rickshaws%20on%20the%20dirt%20road%2C%20their%20harvests%20to%20be%20combined%20in%20large%20piles%20atop%20orange%20and%20blue%20tarpaulin%20mats.%20Traders%20would%20buy%20however%20much%20they%20wanted%20in%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Abdullah%20Sheikh%20wandered%20around%20the%20market%20helping%20farmers%20weigh%20their%20sacks%20and%20traders%20make%20their%20purchases.%20Over%20the%20last%2030%20years%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20become%20well%20acquainted%20with%20the%20space%2C%20as%20his%20turmeric%20processing%20business%20and%20trading%20facilities%20are%20headquartered%20next%20door.%20He%20buys%20most%20of%20his%20turmeric%20from%20this%20market%20and%20processes%20it%20to%20sell%20to%20larger%20food%20manufacturers%20and%20wholesalers%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20his%20turmeric%20trading%20career%2C%20Sheikh%20engaged%20in%20an%20open%20secret%3A%20While%20processing%20raw%20turmeric%20to%20powder%2C%20he%20added%20a%20chemical%20called%20lead%20chromate%20to%20get%20the%20tubers%20to%20glow%20yellow.%20Sheikh%20and%20the%20locals%20refer%20to%20the%20compound%20as%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epeuri%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20nearly%20all%20the%20farmers%20and%20traders%20at%20the%20market%20are%20familiar%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELead%20chromate%20is%20a%20chemical%20used%20in%20paints%20to%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20make%20school%20buses%20yellow%2C%20and%20it%20can%20enhance%20the%20radiance%20of%20turmeric%20roots%2C%20making%20them%20more%20attractive%20to%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20Sheikh%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20exact%20harm%20that%20peuri%20could%20cause.%20That%20changed%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202019%2C%20when%20researchers%20from%20the%20nonprofit%20International%20Center%20for%20Diarrheal%20Disease%20Research%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20or%20ICDDR%2CB%2C%20travelled%20to%20Ataikula%20and%20adjacent%20districts%20in%20the%20northwest%20to%20meet%20with%20Sheikh%20and%20others%20in%20the%20turmeric%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20warned%20them%20that%20consuming%20lead%20chromate%20could%20lead%20to%20kidney%20and%20brain%20damage%20or%20cause%20developmental%20delays%20in%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20point%2C%20the%20spice%20had%20made%20its%20way%20out%20of%20the%20country%3A%20The%20problem%20had%20already%20gone%20global.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20outreach%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20years%20of%20work%20conducted%20by%20an%20international%20group%20of%20researchers%2C%20including%20a%20research%20scientist%20at%20Stanford%20University.%20They%20worked%20together%20with%20the%20ICDDR%2CB%20and%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20Food%20Safety%20Authority%20to%20protect%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20food%20supply%20from%20further%20lead%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impacts%20of%20this%20intervention%20were%20significant%2C%20and%20summarised%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0013935123011325%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20recently%20in%20the%20science%20journal%20Environmental%20Research.%20When%20researchers%20sampled%20and%20tested%20turmeric%20across%20the%20country%20before%20and%20after%20the%20intervention%2C%20the%20level%20of%20adulteration%20in%20this%20one%20study%20dropped%20from%2047%25%20to%200%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28174645%2FUndark-M.A.-Sheikh-1024x576.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28174645%2FUndark-M.A.-Sheikh-1024x576.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28174645%2FUndark-M.A.-Sheikh-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28174645%2FUndark-M.A.-Sheikh.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665683%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFor%20most%20of%20his%20turmeric%20trading%20career%20in%20Ataikula%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Mohammad%20Abdullah%20Sheikh%20added%20lead%20chromate%20to%20the%20spice%20to%20enhance%20its%20economic%20value%20%E2%80%93%20an%20open%20secret%20in%20the%20business.%20But%20then%20he%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20harm%20the%20chemical%20can%20cause.%20Photo%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20%3Cem%3EUndark%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20peuri%20in%20turmeric%20renders%20the%20food%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Fcompliance-enforcement-food%2Feconomically-motivated-adulteration-food-fraud%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEMA%2520also%2520occurs%2520when%2520someone%2Cof%2520EMA%2520as%2520food%2520fraud.%5C%22%3Efraudulent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20done%20purposefully%20to%20alter%20the%20commodity%20for%20economic%20gain.%20Instances%20of%20food%20fraud%20are%20notoriously%20difficult%20to%20resolve%2C%20said%20Michael%20Roberts%2C%20expert%20on%20the%20regulation%20of%20food%20fraud%2C%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Resnick%20Center%20for%20Food%20Law%20and%20Policy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20School%20of%20Law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20the%20economic%20incentives%20just%20aren%E2%80%99t%20there%20for%20authentically%20made%20food.%20Processors%20are%20likely%20to%20increase%20their%20margins%20if%20they%20cheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFighting%20food%20fraud%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20and%20experts%20have%20a%20range%20of%20ideas%20on%20how%20to%20do%20it.%20Some%20approaches%20rely%20heavily%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2Fsep%2F16%2Ffood-fraud-counterfeit-cotton-detectives-untangling-global-supply-chain%5C%22%3Escientific%20testing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0while%20others%20work%20through%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodsafetynews.com%2F2015%2F08%2Fiafp-2015-interview-with-mitchell-weinberg-ceo-of-food-fraud-firm-inscatech%2F%5C%22%3Eundercover%20investigations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20method%2C%20rooting%20out%20food%20fraud%20requires%20constant%20surveillance%20across%20long%20and%20complex%20supply%20chains.%20In%20this%20sense%2C%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20noteworthy%2C%20said%20Roberts%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20project%20to%20eliminate%20lead%20chromate%20from%20turmeric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20unusual%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20campaign%20takes%20place%2C%20whether%20in%20developed%20or%20developing%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20and%20there%20are%20lessons%20from%20this%20case%20study%20that%20could%20be%20applied%20to%20other%20commodities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20native%20to%20South%20Asia%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0turmeric%20has%20been%20used%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK92752%2F%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20both%20a%20culinary%20and%20a%20medicinal%20ingredient.%20In%20Bangladesh%2C%20it%20is%20often%20planted%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20requires%20nine%20to%20ten%20months%20to%20mature%20before%20it%E2%80%99s%20harvested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrecipitation%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%20is%20critical%3A%20A%20generous%20amount%20of%20rain%20will%20allow%20for%20the%20root%20to%20bloom%2C%20shooting%20off%20additional%20roots%2C%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfingers%E2%80%9D%2C%20from%20the%20bulb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEskandar%20Molla%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20northwest%20Bangladesh%2C%20has%20been%20growing%20turmeric%20for%20over%2050%20years.%20He%20sells%20his%20fresh%20turmeric%20fingers%20at%20nearby%20Hazir%20Hat%2C%20an%20open%20air%20market.%20There%2C%20he%20gets%20paid%20a%20market%20rate%20for%20what%20he%20sells%3A%20In%20March%20of%20this%20year%2C%20it%20was%20around%201%2C400%20taka%20(about%20%2413%20USD)%20for%20an%2088-pound%20satchel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiddlemen%2C%20who%20have%20the%20facilities%20to%20boil%20and%20dry%20the%20root%2C%20buy%20it%20from%20him%20and%20other%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20moisture%20out%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20root%20to%20be%20pulsed%20into%20powder.%20Traders%20lay%20out%20a%20single%20layer%20of%20turmeric%20fingers%20in%20vast%2C%20sunny%2C%20open%20fields%20for%20a%20month.%20Workers%20manually%20go%20through%20and%20inspect%20for%20roots%20that%20are%20either%20too%20long%2C%20too%20fat%2C%20or%20too%20skinny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20dried%2C%20the%20turmeric%20fingers%20are%20polished.%20Here%2C%20they%20are%20dumped%20into%20large%20%E2%80%9Cdrums%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20are%20turned%20by%20hand%20or%20motorised.%20This%20continual%20physical%20agitation%20removes%20the%20outer%20skin%20of%20the%20turmeric%20to%20reveal%20the%20true%20colour%20of%20the%20root.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20in%20this%20step%20that%20lead%20chromate%20would%20be%20used%20to%20enhance%20colour.%20Once%20polished%2C%20the%20roots%20are%20then%20ground%20to%20a%20fine%20golden%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28180820%2FUndark-turmeric-drying-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28180820%2FUndark-turmeric-drying-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28180820%2FUndark-turmeric-drying-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28180820%2FUndark-turmeric-drying.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665688%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETurmeric%20drying%20in%20an%20open%20field%20after%20being%20boiled.%20To%20remove%20moisture%2C%20the%20fingers%20are%20spread%20out%20in%20a%20single%20layer%20for%20a%20month.%20Workers%20then%20sort%20through%20the%20spice%20by%20size.%20Photo%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20%3Cem%3EUndark%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28181942%2FUndark-collage-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28181942%2FUndark-collage-1.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28181942%2FUndark-collage-1-300x210.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665691%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EL%3A%20Freshly%20harvested%20turmeric%20in%20Pabna.%20R%3A%20A%20turmeric%20polishing%20machine.%20Photos%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20%3Cem%3EUndark%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20northwest%20districts%20around%20Ataikula%2C%20farmers%20often%20talk%20about%20a%20large%20flood%20in%201988%20that%20damaged%20the%20crop%20and%20darkened%20the%20colour%20of%20the%20roots.%20To%20cope%20with%20a%20bad%20turmeric%20growing%20season%2C%20Bangladeshi%20businesses%20began%20importing%20the%20spice%20from%20India.%20Meanwhile%2C%20to%20remain%20competitive%2C%20Bangladeshi%20processors%20started%20using%20peuri%20to%20disguise%20the%20colour%20of%20the%20water-damaged%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20of%20adulteration%20became%20more%20common%20after%20the%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%2C%20the%20trader%20from%20Ataikula%2C%20recalls%20being%20enthralled%20by%20the%20golden%20glow%20of%20the%20turmeric%20that%20he%20saw%20at%20a%20market%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%20When%20he%20asked%20the%20traders%20about%20it%2C%20they%20told%20him%20to%20go%20to%20India%20to%20learn%20to%20add%20peuri%20during%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20followed%20their%20advice.%20When%20he%20returned%20home%20and%20brought%20his%20haul%20to%20the%20market%2C%20he%20earned%20more%20when%20selling%20turmeric%20polished%20with%20peuri.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwholesalers%20were%20not%20willing%20to%20buy%20if%20there%20was%20no%20chemical%20in%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20turmeric%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20has%20expanded%20widely%2C%20becoming%20something%20of%20a%20global%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fextension.illinois.edu%2Fblogs%2Fsimply-nutritious-quick-and-delicious%2F2019-01-27-turmeric-trendy-spice%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUsed%2520for%2520more%2520than%25205%252C000%2Cmajor%2520ingredient%2520in%2520curry%2520recipes.%5C%22%3Etrend%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Actress%20Gwyneth%20Paltrow%20helped%20boost%20turmeric%E2%80%99s%20stardom%20by%20popularising%20the%20spice-infused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2016%2Fmay%2F11%2Fturmeric-latte-golden-milk-cult-following-alternative-coffee%5C%22%3Egolden%20latte%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Instagram.%20The%20supplement%20industry%20sells%20an%20array%20of%20turmeric%20products%20used%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8572027%2F%5C%22%3Ecurb%20inflammation%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20purportedly%20protect%20against%20high%20cholesterol%20and%20heart%20disease.%20And%20scientists%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F1934578X1300800633%5C%22%3Estudying%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20plant%20for%20chemicals%20that%20might%20help%20treat%20cancer%20and%20other%20challenging%20medical%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20consumers%20worldwide%20may%20have%20unknowingly%20purchased%20a%20contaminated%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELead%20chromate%20is%20comprised%20of%20two%20heavy%20metals%2C%20lead%20and%20chromium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20risks%20of%20lead%20consumption%20are%20well%20documented.%20Continual%20exposure%20can%20cause%20developmental%20and%20neurological%20issues%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Flead%2Fprevention%2Fhealth-effects.htm%5C%22%3Echildren%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20absorb%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Flead-poisoning-and-health%5C%22%3Efour%20to%20five%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20much%20lead%20as%20adults.%20In%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fsite%2Fdoh%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-topics%2Flead-poisoning-adults-and-lead-poisoning.page%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLead%2520exposure%2520can%2520cause%2520high%2Cand%2520loss%2520of%2520sex%2520drive.%5C%22%3Eadults%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20repeated%20lead%20exposure%20is%20linked%20to%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20as%20well%20as%20kidney%20and%20reproductive%20issues.%20Over%20time%2C%20lead%20can%20get%20integrated%20into%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-019-50654-7%5C%22%3Ebones%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20the%20body%20mistakes%20it%20for%20calcium%2C%20owing%20to%20similar%20chemical%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20known%20safe%20level%20of%20lead%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chromium%20in%20lead%20chromate%20poses%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osha.gov%2Fhexavalent-chromium%2Fhealth-effects%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAdverse%2520health%2520effects%2520associated%2520with%2Cskin%2520irritation%252C%2520and%2520erosion%2520and%5C%22%3Ehealth%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20It%20exists%20in%20a%20chemical%20form%20that%E2%80%99s%20known%20to%20be%20cancerous.%20It%20can%20also%20cause%20allergic%20reactions%2C%20respiratory%20issues%20and%20kidney%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20peuri%20in%20turmeric%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20examples%20of%20food%20fraud.%20According%20to%20the%20U.S.%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%2C%20food%20fraud%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Fcompliance-enforcement-food%2Feconomically-motivated-adulteration-food-fraud%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOutside%2520estimates%2520by%2520experts%2520have%2Cas%2520%252440%2520billion%2520a%2520year.%5C%22%3Eaffects%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20least%201%20percent%20of%20the%20global%20food%20industry%20and%20costs%20as%20much%20as%20%2440%20billion%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flaw.ucla.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FPDFs%2FPublications%2F_RES_PUB%2520fraud%2520report.pdf%5C%22%3ECheaper%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20blended%20into%20products%20labelled%20100%20percent%20extra%20virgin%20olive%20oil%2C%20and%20some%20companies%20have%20added%20low-cost%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2016-02-16%2Fthe-parmesan-cheese-you-sprinkle-on-your-penne-could-be-wood%5C%22%3Ecellulose%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20grated%20cheese.%20Sometimes%20the%20fraud%20poses%20a%20safety%20issue.%20Baby%20formula%20and%20pet%20food%20manufacturers%20have%20had%20to%20recall%20products%20containing%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fscience%2Fmelamine%5C%22%3Emelamine%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20caused%20kidney%20failure.%20And%20spice%20producers%20have%20sold%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allergicliving.com%2F2015%2F01%2F22%2Fpeanut-contaminated-cumin-leads-to-massive-allergy-recall%2F%5C%22%3Ecumin%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20peanut%20powder%20as%20filler%2C%20putting%20individuals%20with%20peanut%20allergies%20at%20risk%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodpoisonjournal.com%2Ffood-poisoning-information%2Ftexas-woman-files-suit-against-reily-foods-over-spice-products-tainted-with-peanut-and-almond-allergens%2F%5C%22%3Eanaphylactic%20shock%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20began%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20about%20turmeric%20around%202011.%20In%20April%20of%20that%20year%2C%20Archer%20Farms%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodsafetynews.com%2F2011%2F04%2Fturmeric-recalled-due-to-excessive-lead-levels%2F%5C%22%3Erecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0its%20turmeric%2C%20which%20was%20sold%20nationwide%20at%20Target%20and%20Top%20Food%20stores%2C%20for%20having%20high%20levels%20of%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20continued%20surveillance%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B35XQ_SJbEm4Rkk2Zl8waHZxUjQ%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%26resourcekey%3D0-b1M7FbJg3stZo9WrIsGshA%5C%22%3Etesting%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20food%20safety%20inspectors%20at%20the%20New%20York%20State%20Department%20of%20Health%20identified%20lead%20in%20turmeric%20sold%20by%20Pran%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20company.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20FDA%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessdata.fda.gov%2Fcms_ia%2Fimportalert_1167.html%5C%22%3Eissued%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0more%20than%20a%20dozen%20alerts%20for%20turmeric%20products%20from%20South%20Asia%20for%20high%20lead%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20recalls%20notwithstanding%2C%20turmeric%20purchased%20in%20the%20United%20States%20tends%20to%20have%20lower%20levels%20of%20lead%2C%20said%20Paromita%20Hore%2C%20the%20director%20of%20environmental%20exposure%20assessment%20and%20education%20in%20New%20York%20City%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Mental%20Hygiene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20coauthored%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.lww.com%2Fjphmp%2FFulltext%2F2019%2F01001%2FA_Spoonful_of_Lead__A_10_Year_Look_at_Spices_as_a.11.aspx%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tested%20nearly%201%2C500%20samples%20of%20spice%20products.%20The%20turmeric%20purchased%20abroad%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20India%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Morocco%20%E2%80%93%20had%20the%20highest%20lead%20concentrations%2C%20meaning%20that%20people%20all%20over%20the%20world%20could%20have%20been%20affected.%20This%20disparity%2C%20the%20study%20explained%2C%20may%20have%20been%20due%20to%20the%20adulteration%20of%20spices%20in%20countries%20with%20poor%20regulatory%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29204317%2FUndark-Hazir-Hat-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29204317%2FUndark-Hazir-Hat-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29204317%2FUndark-Hazir-Hat-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29204317%2FUndark-Hazir-Hat.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETurmeric%20for%20sale%20at%20Hazir%20Hat%2C%20an%20open%20air%20market.%20The%20root%2C%20native%20to%20South%20Asia%2C%20has%20been%20used%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20as%20both%20a%20culinary%20and%20a%20medicinal%20ingredient.%20Photo%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20%3Cem%3EUndark%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamilies%20in%20the%20U.S.%20were%20affected%2C%20too%2C%20through%20the%20informal%20movement%20of%20spices%20that%20happens%20when%20they%20visit%20their%20home%20countries%20and%20bring%20products%20back%20to%20the%20U.S.%20This%20practice%20circumvents%20the%20regulations%20in%20place%20for%20commercially%20imported%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudies%20conducted%20in%20Boston%2C%20New%20York%20City%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Colorado%20and%20Washington%20have%20all%20found%20a%20connection%20between%20consumption%20of%20lead-tainted%20turmeric%20(mostly%20procured%20from%20markets%20overseas)%20and%20elevated%20blood-lead%20levels.%20Still%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20challenging%20to%20calculate%20exactly%20how%20much%20lead%20in%20spices%20is%20problematic%20for%20human%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20only%20food%20in%20which%20the%20FDA%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fregulatory-information%2Fsearch-fda-guidance-documents%2Fguidance-industry-lead-candy-likely-be-consumed-frequently-small-children%23ftn2%5C%22%3Eestablished%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20maximum%20level%20of%20lead%20was%20candy%3A%200.1%20parts%20per%20million%20for%20small%20children.%20It%20took%20the%20agency%20about%2016%20years%20to%20announce%20another%20update%2C%20outlining%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fpress-announcements%2Ffda-announces-action-levels-lead-categories-processed-baby-foods%5C%22%3Eguidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20other%20foods%20commonly%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fundark.org%2F2023%2F05%2F15%2Fthe-daunting-task-of-cutting-heavy-metals-from-baby-food%2F%5C%22%3Econsumed%20by%20babies%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20young%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFruits%2C%20the%20agency%20said%2C%20should%20not%20exceed%2010%20parts%20per%20billion%20in%20lead%2C%20and%20root%20vegetables%20and%20dried%20cereals%20should%20not%20exceed%2020%20parts%20per%20billion.%20This%20guideline%20did%20not%20discuss%20spices%2C%20and%20no%20maximum%20limits%20for%20lead%20are%20noted%20for%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20lead%20levels%20detected%20in%20turmeric%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasafdo.com%2Fresources%2FDocuments%2FLead-in-Spices.pdf%5C%22%3Eranged%20from%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A028%20to%20146%20parts%20per%20million%2C%20magnitudes%20more%20than%20the%20FDA%E2%80%99s%20established%20acceptable%20levels%20for%20other%20foods.%20(The%20FDA%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20even%20though%20it%20monitors%20levels%20of%20lead%20in%20food%2C%20and%20knows%20about%20the%20turmeric%20recalls%20owing%20to%20high%20lead%20levels%2C%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20set%20a%20limit%20for%20lead%20in%20spices.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETom%20Tarantelli%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Market%E2%80%99s%20former%20senior%20food%20chemist%2C%20has%20estimated%20that%20children%20in%20families%20that%20use%20turmeric%20regularly%20could%20be%20consuming%203%20to%204%20grams%20a%20day%20of%20that%20spice%20alone%2C%20suggesting%20that%20these%20kids%20are%20consuming%20far%20more%20spice%20than%2C%20say%2C%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20health%20surveys%20in%20Colorado%20have%20detected%20blood%20lead%20levels%20of%20over%2024%20mcg%2FdL%20%E2%80%93%20equivalent%20to%20about%20630%20grains%20of%20sand%20in%20a%20filled%20bathtub%20%E2%80%93%20in%20children%20of%20families%20who%20regularly%20consumed%20spices%20high%20in%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centers%20for%20Medicare%20and%20Medicaid%20Services%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medicaid.gov%2Fmedicaid%2Fbenefits%2Fearly-and-periodic-screening-diagnostic-and-treatment%2Flead-screening%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Erequires%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20children%20on%20Medicaid%20get%20tested%20for%20lead%20at%20ages%20one%20and%20two.%20The%20U.S.%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Flead%2Fprevention%2Ftesting-children-for-lead-poisoning.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChildren%2520enrolled%2520in%2520Medicaid%2520are%2Chigh%252Drisk%2520neighborhoods%2520and%2520children.%5C%22%3Erecommends%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20same%20for%20those%20not%20on%20the%20government%20program%20but%20who%20are%20at%20risk%20for%20exposure%2C%20but%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20happen%2C%20and%20turmeric-induced%20lead%20poisoning%20might%20be%20under-diagnosed%2C%20said%20Jessica%20Ivers%2C%20a%20general%20paediatrician%20at%20The%20Polyclinic%20in%20Seattle%2C%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recently%20tested%20a%20patient%20who%20had%20immigrated%20to%20the%20U.S.%20in%202019%20and%20was%20exhibiting%20developmental%20delays.%20%E2%80%9CLo%20and%20behold%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20lead%20level%20was%20high%2C%20she%20said.%20And%20the%20culprit%3F%20The%20turmeric%20powder%20that%20the%20family%20had%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20U.S.%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20period%20of%2018%20months%2C%20in%20her%20small%20practice%20of%20at%20most%202%2C000%20kids%2C%20Ivers%20said%20she%20had%20three%20cases%20of%20elevated%20lead%2C%20all%20in%20families%20from%20India%20and%20all%20related%20to%20the%20consumption%20of%20spices.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20prevalence%20is%20three%20in%202%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added%2C%20physicians%20are%20missing%20a%20lot%20of%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJenna%20Forsyth%20knew%20nothing%20about%20the%20practice%20of%20adding%20lead%20chromate%20to%20turmeric%20in%202014%2C%20when%20she%20started%20her%20Ph.D.%20in%20environment%20and%20resources%20at%20Stanford%20University.%20Excited%20to%20continue%20her%20masters%20research%20on%20water%20and%20sanitation%2C%20she%20sought%20out%20working%20with%20Stephen%20Luby%2C%20a%20world%20expert%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20arrived%2C%20Luby%20instead%20pointed%20Forsyth%20to%20a%20conundrum%20he%20was%20encountering%20in%20his%20work%20in%20Bangladesh%3A%20In%20a%20rural%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20pregnant%20women%20and%20children%20had%20high%20levels%20of%20lead%20in%20their%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20none%20of%20the%20usual%20suspects%20of%20lead%20exposure.%20There%20were%20no%20nearby%20battery%20recycling%20plants%20and%20families%20didn%E2%80%99t%20paint%20their%20homes.%20How%20could%20this%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20201px)%2085vw%2C%20201px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29205344%2FJenna-Forsyth-201x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22201%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29205344%2FJenna-Forsyth-201x300.jpg%20201w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29205344%2FJenna-Forsyth.jpg%20350w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJenna%20Forsyth.%20Photo%3A%20woods.stanford.edu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForsyth%20and%20her%20Bangladeshi%20colleagues%20had%20a%20slew%20of%20hypotheses.%20Maybe%20the%20lead%20was%20coming%20from%20jewelry%20or%20food%20storage%20containers.%20Or%20perhaps%20it%20came%20from%20clay%2C%20soil%2C%20or%20ash%20that%20the%20mothers%20were%20exposed%20to%20during%20pregnancy.%20Rice%20was%20another%20possibility%2C%20as%20the%20staple%20crop%20could%20have%20absorbed%20lead%20from%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForsyth%20and%20her%20colleagues%20sampled%20and%20tested%20all%20of%20these.%20She%20vividly%20remembers%20the%20first%20summer%20of%20her%20Ph.D.%2C%20as%20she%20baked%20and%20ground%20rice%20into%20a%20pulp%20to%20test%20for%20lead%20in%20a%20sweltering%20laboratory%20in%20rural%20Bangladesh.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20obvious%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForsyth%20also%20scoured%20the%20literature%20and%20eventually%20discovered%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F25214856%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0published%20in%202014.%20A%20team%20that%20included%20researchers%20from%20Harvard%E2%80%99s%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20had%20reported%20that%20contaminated%20turmeric%20was%20contributing%20to%20elevated%20lead%20levels%20in%20children%20in%20rural%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20intriguing%2C%20Forsyth%20thought%2C%20as%20the%20families%20she%20was%20working%20with%20were%20growing%20their%20own%20food%2C%20but%20not%20their%20own%20spices.%20She%20went%20back%20to%20the%20homes%20she%20had%20sampled%20from%20earlier.%20Seventeen%20out%20of%2020%20gave%20her%20samples%20of%20turmeric%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20Forsyth%20found%20the%20culprit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20showed%20Luby%20her%20results%2C%20he%20was%20sceptical%20and%20encouraged%20her%20to%20gather%20more%20data.%20So%20Forsyth%20and%20her%20colleagues%20used%20a%20method%20called%20isotopic%20analysis%2C%20which%20uses%20chemical%20clues%20to%20definitively%20determine%20the%20source%20of%20lead.%20When%20they%20compared%20the%20isotopes%20of%20lead%20in%20the%20blood%20to%20those%20from%20other%20possible%20contaminants%2C%20the%20isotopes%20most%20closely%20matched%20that%20of%20turmeric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20this%20discovery%2C%20Forsyth%20and%20her%20Bangladeshi%20collaborators%20at%20the%20International%20Center%20for%20Diarrheal%20Disease%20Research%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20met%20with%20government%20officials%20from%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Agricultural%20Authority%20to%20understand%20how%20turmeric%20was%20produced%20and%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20these%20conversations%2C%20and%20from%20conversations%20with%20others%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20they%20identified%20nine%20regions%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20eight%20of%20which%20contribute%20almost%20half%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20turmeric%20for%20domestic%20use%20and%20export.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20then%20interviewed%20turmeric%20producers%20and%20food%20safety%20inspectors%20in%20each%20district.%20They%20also%20collected%20samples%20of%20pigments%20and%20turmeric%20%E2%80%94%20powdered%2C%20polished%2C%20unpolished%2C%20labelled%2C%20unlabelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20140%20turmeric%20samples%20collected%20nationwide%2C%20Forsyth%20and%20her%20colleagues%20found%20that%20lead%20concentrations%20were%20highest%20for%20polished%20bulbs%20and%20for%20some%20turmeric%20powders%2C%20with%20two%20samples%20of%20powdered%20turmeric%20exceeding%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20limit%20for%20lead%20in%20turmeric%20powder%2C%20at%208.4%20ppm%20and%2026.6%20ppm.%20(At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20study%2C%20the%20limit%20was%202.5%20ppm%3B%20it%20has%20since%20been%20raised%20to%205%20ppm.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20visited%20mills%2C%20and%20sometimes%20found%20sacks%20of%20the%20pigment%20on-site.%20They%20sampled%20dust%20from%20the%20polishing%20machine%20and%20from%20the%20floors%20of%20the%20mill.%20If%20there%20was%20about%20one%20part%20of%20lead%20to%20chromium%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dead%20giveaway%20that%20the%20adulterant%20was%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20interviews%2C%20they%20also%20understood%20the%20motive%3A%20Brighter%20roots%20led%20to%20more%20profit%2C%20and%20adulterating%20with%20a%20consistently%20bright%20paint%20agent%20could%20disguise%20poorer-quality%20roots.%20The%20findings%20from%20this%20study%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0013935119305195%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Bangladesh%20Food%20Safety%20Authority.%20The%20agency%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Syeda%20Sarwar%20Jahan%2C%20was%20immediately%20concerned.%20She%20decided%20to%20spearhead%20a%20massive%20public%20information%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20and%20international%20news%20outlets%20disseminated%20the%20findings%20from%20Forsyth%E2%80%99s%20new%20studies%20to%20create%20public%20awareness.%20The%20researchers%20met%20with%20businesses%20to%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20the%20risks%20of%20lead%20in%20turmeric.%20BFSA%20posted%20notices%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20largest%20wholesale%20spice%20market%2C%20Shyambazar.%20The%20flyers%20warned%20people%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20lead%20and%20that%20anyone%20caught%20selling%20turmeric%20adulterated%20with%20lead%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20also%20raided%20Shyambazar%20using%20a%20machine%20called%20an%20X-ray%20fluorescence%20analyser%20which%20can%20quickly%20detect%20lead%20in%20spices.%20Nearly%202%2C000%20pounds%20of%20turmeric%20was%20seized%20in%20the%20raid%20and%20two%20wholesalers%20were%20fined%20800%2C000%20taka%2C%20more%20than%20%249%2C000%20USD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20team%20went%20back%20again%20to%20collect%20samples%20to%20see%20how%20their%20intervention%20had%20fared.%20Only%20about%205%20percent%20of%20157%20samples%20were%20found%20to%20be%20adulterated%20with%20lead%20chromate%2C%20down%20from%20nearly%2050%20percent%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20researchers%20conducted%20a%20sampling%20spree%20again%20in%202021%2C%20they%20found%20that%20the%20use%20of%20lead%20chromate%20had%20practically%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20a%20rainy%20Sunday%20%3C%2Fspan%3Emorning%20in%20March%2C%20Shyambazar%20was%20already%20bustling.%20Vendors%20selling%20eggplant%2C%20garlic%2C%20onion%2C%20greens%20and%20fruits%20lined%20the%20side%20of%20the%20market%20facing%20the%20Buriganga%20River%2C%20which%20connects%20the%20capital%20city%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20by%20an%20intricate%20path%20of%20waterways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20vendors%20were%20offloading%20truckloads%20of%20pineapple%2C%20as%20rickshaws%2C%20motorbikes%2C%20and%20cars%20drove%20neck-to-neck%2C%20negotiating%20for%20space%20along%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarrow%20passageways%20connect%20the%20bustling%20vegetable%20market%20to%20its%20interior%2C%20where%20dried%20goods%2C%20including%20spices%2C%20are%20found.%20The%20fragrant%2C%20sharp%20scents%20of%20chili%2C%20cumin%20and%20turmeric%20travel%20down%20the%20slick%2C%20narrow%20walkways%20as%20wholesalers%20and%20buyers%20manoeuvre%20about%20with%20large%20burlap%20sacks%20atop%20their%20heads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20turmeric%20wholesalers%20selling%20in%20Shyambazar%20have%20been%20at%20it%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years.%20Law%20enforcement%2C%20they%20said%2C%20had%20only%20showed%20up%20for%20the%20turmeric.%20No%20other%20spices%2C%20they%20noted%2C%20have%20ever%20come%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210237%2FUndark-Shyambazar-spices-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210237%2FUndark-Shyambazar-spices-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210237%2FUndark-Shyambazar-spices-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210237%2FUndark-Shyambazar-spices.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665839%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarrow%20passageways%20connect%20the%20bustling%20vegetable%20market%20at%20Shyambazar%20to%20its%20interior%2C%20where%20dried%20goods%2C%20including%20spices%2C%20are%20found.%20Photo%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20Undark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210554%2FUndark-collage-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210554%2FUndark-collage-2.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210554%2FUndark-collage-2-300x210.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665840%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EL%3A%20Fresh%20turmeric%20for%20sale%20at%20Shyambazar.%20Removal%20of%20the%20pale%20skin%20during%20the%20polishing%20process%20uncovers%20the%20root%E2%80%99s%20prized%20golden%20colour.%20R%3A%20Bags%20of%20turmeric%20stored%20at%20a%20wholesaler%20at%20Shyambazar.%20According%20to%20such%20wholesalers%2C%20law%20enforcement%20has%20only%20ever%20scrutinised%20turmeric%20at%20the%20market.%20Photos%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20%3Cem%3EUndark%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202019%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20intervention%20against%20lead%20chromate%20use%20in%20turmeric%2C%20the%20Bangladesh%20Food%20Safety%20Authority%20printed%20and%20distributed%20an%20estimated%2050%2C000%20copies%20of%20green%20flyers%2C%20that%20they%20shared%20with%20traders%20and%20plastered%20around%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20sceptical%20of%20fingers%20that%20appear%20too%20bright%20and%20yellow%2C%20it%20advised%2C%20and%20if%20the%20yellow%20dusting%20from%20turmeric%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20off%20easily%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20likely%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20played.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20those%20flyers%20are%20now%20gone.%20One%20trader%2C%20Mohammad%20Mosharof%20Khokon%2C%20who%20has%20been%20selling%20turmeric%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20kept%20a%20copy%20under%20the%20glass%20top%20of%20his%20desk.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20he%20was%20compliant%2C%20albeit%20nervous%20for%20the%20researchers%20to%20scan%20his%20satchels%20of%20spice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20machine%20could%20show%20some%20error%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20about%20the%20XRF%2C%20%E2%80%9Cand%20then%20I%20would%20lose%20my%20business.%E2%80%9D%20Despite%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20when%20authorities%20could%20show%20up%20again%2C%20Khokon%20said%20that%20the%20enforcement%20is%20a%20good%20thing%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20ensures%20the%20quality%20and%20purity%20of%20the%20product.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShoraf%20Ali%20Biswash%20was%20one%20of%20the%20traders%20who%20had%20turmeric%20from%20his%20warehouse%20seized%20during%20the%20raid%20and%20paid%20a%20fine%20of%20400%2C000%20taka%20(approximately%20%243%2C700).%20For%20him%2C%20selling%20turmeric%20is%20a%20family%20affair%3A%20His%20brother%20has%20a%20polishing%20mill%20near%20Pabna%20and%20for%20years%2C%20used%20peuri%20to%20polish%20the%20roots%20that%20Biswash%20then%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20fine%2C%20Biswash%20believes%20the%20increased%20surveillance%20is%20also%20for%20the%20best.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20100%25%20good%20because%20the%20chemical%20was%20bad%20for%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20At%20home%2C%20he%20was%20feeding%20his%20family%20turmeric%20polished%20with%20lead%20chromate%20and%20immediately%20stopped%20once%20he%20learned%20the%20health%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crackdown%20on%20turmeric%20in%202019%20may%2C%20in%20part%2C%20explain%20why%20the%20use%20of%20lead%20chromate%20in%20polishing%20turmeric%20has%20since%20decreased.%20It%20was%20a%20punishable%20crime%2C%20and%20although%20there%20was%20only%20one%20raid%2C%20people%20now%20know%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20risk%20of%20getting%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20spring%2C%20Undark%20collected%20three%20samples%20of%20polished%20turmeric%20fingers%20from%20Shyambazar%20and%20brought%20them%20back%20to%20get%20tested%20at%20NVL%20Labs%2C%20a%20Seattle-based%20company%20that%20tests%20for%20environmental%20contaminants%20including%20lead.%20In%20this%20admittedly%20small%20sample%2C%20none%20of%20the%20turmeric%20had%20lead%20levels%20of%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210925%2FUndark-flyer-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210925%2FUndark-flyer-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210925%2FUndark-flyer-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29210925%2FUndark-flyer.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Food%20Safety%20Authority%E2%80%99s%202019%20flyer%2C%20stored%20under%20glass%20on%20Mohammad%20Mosharof%20Khokon%E2%80%99s%20desk.%20During%20the%20BFSA%20raid%2C%20he%20was%20compliant%2C%20but%20nervous%20that%20the%20machines%20used%20to%20scan%20his%20spices%20could%20be%20incorrect.%20Most%20of%20the%20flyers%20are%20now%20gone%2C%20and%20no%20other%20raids%20have%20been%20conducted.%20Photo%3A%20Wudan%20Yan%20for%20%3Cem%3EUndark%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20government%20officials%20and%20researchers%20say%20that%20enforcement%20and%20surveillance%20must%20be%20maintained.%20%E2%80%9CA%20one-time%20conviction%20is%20not%20sufficient%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Jahan%2C%20who%20has%20since%20moved%20on%20from%20the%20Bangladesh%20Food%20Safety%20Authority.%20Follow-up%20is%20required%20as%20she%20has%20%E2%80%9Cseen%20such%20criminals%20go%20back%20to%20doing%20what%20they%20did%20even%20after%20facing%20consequences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonzur%20Morshed%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20member%20of%20BFSA%2C%20says%20that%20the%20agency%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20procuring%20handheld%20X-ray%20fluorescence%20analysers%20to%20distribute%20to%20districts%20around%20Bangladesh%20so%20local%20authorities%20can%20continue%20monitoring%20the%20use%20of%20lead%20chromate%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20BFSA%20aims%20to%20inspect%20over%207%2C000%20markets%20and%20food%20establishments%20for%20violations%20of%20food%20safety%2C%20with%20turmeric%20being%20one%20of%20the%20products%20that%20will%20be%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForsyth%20is%20heartened%20by%20the%20impact%20that%20she%20and%20her%20colleagues%20have%20had%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20she%20wants%20to%20replicate%20these%20methods%20%E2%80%93%20studying%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20understanding%20the%20incentives%20for%20adulteration%2C%20and%20creating%20interventions%20to%20dissuade%20the%20use%20of%20lead%20chromate%20%E2%80%93%20in%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20reproducing%20this%20success%20is%20already%20posing%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20easy%2C%20obviously%2C%20to%20collect%20data%20of%20spices%20and%20analyse%20them%20and%20understand%20the%20patterns%20and%20where%20the%20high%20levels%20of%20lead%20are.%20That%E2%80%99s%20been%20straightforward%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Forsyth.%20Identifying%20government%20officials%20who%20can%20advocate%20for%20and%20run%20an%20intervention%20has%20been%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnding%20food%20fraud%20entirely%20for%20any%20commodity%20is%20a%20huge%20challenge%2C%20said%20Roberts%2C%20the%20food%20fraud%20expert%20from%20UCLA.%20Regulatory%20agencies%20in%20different%20countries%20need%20to%20set%20clear%20standards%2C%20enable%20constant%20testing%20and%20surveillance%2C%20and%20be%20willing%20to%20enforce%20penalties%20when%20someone%20has%20committed%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20constant%20vigilance%20can%20be%20expensive%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20and%20the%20economic%20incentive%20to%20cheat%20is%20going%20to%20remain.%20As%20such%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20if%20this%20problem%20pops%20up%20again.%E2%80%9D%20Still%2C%20many%20of%20the%20interventions%20used%20in%20Bangladesh%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20other%20food%20communities%20that%20have%20a%20history%20of%20fraud%2C%20Roberts%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-offset%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20have%20good%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Roberts.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20case%2C%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20blessing%20for%20Bangladesh.%E2%80%9D%20And%2C%20importantly%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cconsumers%20have%20to%20care.%20And%20in%20this%20case%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20pretty%20clear%20that%20consumers%20should%20care%20because%20of%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bangladesh%2C%20even%20those%20who%20have%20committed%20a%20crime%20see%20this%20crackdown%20on%20lead%20chromate%20use%20as%20a%20net%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20said%20he%20had%20felt%20helpless%20to%20change%20direction%20before%20the%20crackdown.%20Although%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20precise%20health%20impacts%20of%20the%20lead%20chromate%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%E2%80%99s%20common%20sense%20that%20chemicals%20are%20harmful.%E2%80%9D%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20never%20used%20peuri-laced%20turmeric%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20Allah%20that%20I%20used%20it%20in%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalled.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20hurt%20me%2C%20sometimes%2C%20to%20do%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shyambazar%20was%20raided%2C%20Sheikh%20knew%20he%20had%20to%20stop.%20Now%2C%20he%20can%20rest%20easy%3A%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20economic%20incentive%20to%20adulterate%20his%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20his%20polishing%20mill%2C%20Sheikh%20held%20up%20a%20basket%20of%20polished%20turmeric%2C%20ready%20to%20be%20shuttled%20along%20to%20the%20next%20set%20of%20hands%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%20The%20roots%20were%20a%20light%20gold%2C%20not%20as%20aggressively%20bright%20as%20they%20used%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20happy%20with%20this%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20in%20Bangladesh%20is%20happier%20with%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWudan%20Yan%20is%20an%20award-winning%20independent%20journalist%20in%20Seattle%20covering%20science%20and%20society.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20supported%20in%20part%20by%20grants%20from%20the%20Pulitzer%20Center%20on%20Crisis%20Reporting%20and%20the%20UC%20Berkeley%20Food%20%26amp%3B%20Farming%20Fellowship.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20Ali%20Ahsan%2C%20a%20Bangladesh-based%20producer%2C%20translated%20interviews%20and%20coordinated%20logistics%20for%20meetings%20with%20farmers%20and%20traders.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs-01.loggly.com%2Finputs%2F4a05953f-1607-4284-825e-7df393822342.gif%3Fpostid%3D78633%26title%3DThe-Vice-of-Spice%3A-Confronting-Lead-Tainted-Turmeric%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690646167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28174539%2FUndark-turmeric-lead-photo.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fthe-vice-of-spice-confronting-lead-tainted-turmeric%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Traders%20in%20Bangladesh%20used%20lead%20chromate%20to%20enhance%20the%20spice%E2%80%99s%20appearance.%20Then%20scientists%20and%20policymakers%20stepped%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fthe-vice-of-spice-confronting-lead-tainted-turmeric%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starlink%20has%20become%20the%20'blood'%20of%20Ukraine's%20communication%20infrastructure%2C%20but%20officials%20are%20reportedly%20growing%20concerned%20about%20relying%20on%20Elon%20Musk's%20tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224903%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20gather%20around%20a%20table%20with%20an%20internet%20router%20to%20use%20their%20smartphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c51ebccf07780019671cd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223677%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EResidents%20of%20Kherson%2C%20Ukraine%20gather%20to%20use%20Starlink%20internet%20in%20November%202022.%3Cp%3EValentyn%20Ogirenko%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20Ukrainian%20official%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20Starlink%20satellites%20are%20vital%20to%20their%20communication%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20he%20also%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20Ukraine's%20overd