cellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20stood%20out.%20Mansoor%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20BJP%20MLC%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20was%20also%20appointed%20as%20one%20of%20the%20vice-presidents%20%E2%80%93%20a%20move%20that%20is%20being%20read%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20outreach%20towards%20Pashmanda%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERadha%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20former%20Union%20minister%20and%20Bihar%20MP%2C%20has%20also%20been%20dropped%20as%20one%20of%20the%20vice-presidents%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20his%20home%20state.%20Anil%20Antony%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20stalwart%20A.K.%20Antony%20son%20who%20recently%20joined%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20brought%20in%20as%20one%20of%20the%20new%20secretaries%20of%20the%20saffron%20party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20development%2C%20Gorakhpur%20leader%20Radha%20Mohan%20Agarwal%20was%20also%20promoted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20national%20general%20secretaries.%20Agarwal%2C%20who%20had%20represented%20Gorakhpur%20(Urban)%20seat%20since%202002%20was%20asked%20to%20vacate%20his%20constituency%20for%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls.%20But%20he%20was%20soon%20made%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20%E2%80%93%20a%20move%20observers%20say%20was%20meant%20to%20placate%20Agarwal.%20He%20was%20also%20given%20the%20responsibility%20to%20oversee%20the%20state%20units%20of%20Kerala%20and%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgarwal%20is%20widely%20known%20as%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20friend-turned-rival%20in%20Gorakhpur.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20openly%20protested%20against%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20state%20administration%20and%20Gorakhpur%20MP%20Ravi%20Kishan%20for%20mismanagement%20of%20floods%20and%20other%20problems.%20By%20appointing%20him%20as%20a%20national%20general%20secretary%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20important%20organisation%20position%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20has%20promoted%20yet%20another%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20rival%20in%20the%20party.%20Earlier%2C%20another%20rival%20of%20Adityanath%2C%20Shiv%20Pratap%20Shukla%2C%20was%20also%20appointed%20as%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20party%20decisions%20were%20taken%20at%20a%20four-hour-long%20meeting%20on%20Friday.%20Chaired%20by%20party%20president%20J.P.Nadda%2C%20the%20meeting%20held%20discussions%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20strategies%2C%20its%20outreach%20programmes%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMaha%20Jansampark%20Abhiyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20its%20progress%20in%20poll-bound%20states%20ahead%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20polls.%20It%20was%20attended%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%20B.L.%20Santosh%2C%20national%20joint%20secretary%20V.Saitsh%2C%20general%20secretaries%20Arun%20Singh%2C%20Sunil%20Bansal%2C%20Vinod%20Tawde%2C%20Tarun%20Chugh%2C%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20Delhi%20Shaukeen%2C%20and%20Dushyant%20Gautam%20among%20others%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fbjp-president-j-p-nadda-overhauls-partys-team-of-central-office-bearers-13-vice-presidents-9-general-secretaries-in-new-list%2Farticleshow%2F102224695.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leaders%20especially%20discussed%20electoral%20strategies%20in%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20all%20of%20which%20will%20have%20their%20assembly%20elections%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20party%20had%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-new