eave-you-stunned-4251249%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Four%20Years%20Since%20General%20Election%2C%20Centre%20Yet%20to%20Obtain%20Info%20on%20EVM-VVPAT%20'Discrepancy'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F09044607%2Fvvpat-evm.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20parliamentary%20panel%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20provide%20a%20reply%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20after%20it%20promised%20parliament%20that%20it%20would%20obtain%20information%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20about%20possible%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20tallies%20during%20the%202019%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20on%20Government%20Assurances%20tabled%20its%20report%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday%20regarding%20pending%20assurances%20pertaining%20to%20the%20Law%20and%20Justice%20Ministry.%20It%20referred%20to%20an%20unstarred%20question%20on%20whether%20any%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20EVM%20and%20VVPAT%20counts%20was%20found%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20if%20so%2C%20what%20corrective%20measures%20had%20been%20taken.%20The%20question%20was%20asked%20on%20June%2026%2C%202019%2C%20and%20the%20government%20had%20back%20then%20said%20that%20information%20was%20being%20collected%20and%20would%20be%20laid%20on%20the%20table%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20four%20years%20have%20passed%20and%20no%20information%20of%20such%20kind%20has%20been%20forthcoming%2C%20the%20committee%20pointed%20out.%20It%20also%20added%20that%20identifying%20such%20issues%20is%20necessary%20for%20the%20security%20of%20the%20voting%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Rajendra%20Agrawal%2C%20was%20told%20by%20the%20Law%20Ministry%20that%20it%20had%20asked%20the%20poll%20body%20for%20the%20required%20information%20on%20March%2012%2C%202020%2C%20and%20had%20sent%20reminders%20on%20September%203%2C%202020%2C%20February%2019%2C%202021%2C%20October%207%2C%202021%2C%20November%2026%2C%202021%20and%20June%203%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20requisite%20information%20from%20the%20EC%20is%20still%20awaited%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F4-yrs-since-ls-polls-ec-yet-to-give-details-of-any-discrepancy-between-evm-vvpat-count-8865739%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legislative%20department%20secretary%20in%20January%20this%20year%20had%20said%20that%20the%20EC%20had%20been%20called%2C%20but%20it%20could%20not%20attend%20as%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Chaving%20discussions%20with%20some%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D.%20The%20committee%20then%20gave%20the%20ministry%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20extension%20to%20fulfil%20the%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Committee%20note%20that%20finding%20discrepancies%20between%20EVMs%20and%20VVPAT%20is%20a%20crucial%20aspect%20of%20ensuring%20the%20integrity%20and%20transparency%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%20The%20Committee%20feels%20that%20the%20need%20for%20identifying%20such%20issues%20is%20all%20the%20more%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20and%20reliability%20of%20the%20voting%20process.%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20are%20designed%20to%20provide%20an%20accurate%20reflection%20of%20voters%E2%80%99%20choices%E2%80%A6The%20Committee%2C%20however%2C%20regret%20to%20note%20that%20precious%20little%20has%20been%20done%20in%20this%20direction%E2%80%A6The%20Committee%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20to%20note%20that%20the%20requisite%20information%20is%20still%20awaited%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20tabled%20by%20the%20committee%20in%20the%20parliament%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20blamed%20the%20delay%20in%20obtaining%20requisite%20information%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20coordination%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20law%20ministry%20and%20the%20poll%20body.%20The%20panel%20also%20instructed%20the%20legislative%20department%20to%20prioritise%20the%20matter%20to%20ensure%20that%20information%20from%20the%20EC%20is%20available%20without%20any%20further%20delay%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Indian%20electoral%20history%2C%20all%20EVMs%20were%20covered%20by%20VVPATs%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%20A%20VVPAT%20lets%20a%20voter%20see%20a%20paper%20slip%20printed%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20for%20a%20period%20of%20seven%20seconds%2C%20displaying%20the%20name%20and%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20selected%20candidate.%20It%20then%20drops%20into%20a%20sealed%20drop%20box%20of%20the%20VVPAT.%20According%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20guidelines%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20verifies%20VVPAT%20slips%20in%20five%20randomly%20selected%20polling%20stations%20in%20each%20Assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20has%20recently%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20seeking%20directions%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20to%20cross-verify%20the%20count%20in%20EVMs%20with%20the%20VVPAT%20slips.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20way%20for%20any%20of%20the%20voters%20to%20verify%20that%20their%20vote%20has%20actually%20been%20%E2%80%98counted%20as%20recorded%E2%80%99%20because%20there%20is%20no%20procedure%20provided%20for%20by%20the%20EC%20for%20them%20to%20match%20the%20VVPATs%20that%20they%20had%20certified%20as%20being%20%E2%80%98recorded%20as%20cast%E2%80%99%20with%20what%20is%20actually%20counted%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ADR%20petition%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20ADR%20petition%2C%20issued%20directions%20to%20send%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20petition%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20and%20asked%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690632596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F09044607%2Fvvpat-evm.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffour-years-since-general-election-centre-yet-to-obtain-info-on-evm-vvpat-discrepancy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20Government%20Assurances%20told%20the%20Law%20Ministry%20to%20prioritise%20the%20matter%20without%20any%20delay.%20It%20said%20the%20issue%20is%20crucial%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20of%20the%20voting%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffour-years-since-general-election-centre-yet-to-obtain-info-on-evm-vvpat-discrepancy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Constitution%20Benches%20Have%20Disposed%20of%20Fewer%20Cases%20Over%20the%20Decades%3A%20Law%20Ministry%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25123828%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_03.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Data%20presented%20by%20the%20Union%20law%20ministry%20in%20parliament%20shows%20that%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20disposed%20of%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20constitution%20benches%20has%20decreased%20over%20the%20decades%20since%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20decade%20between%201960%20and%201969%20saw%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20benches%20dispose%20of%20a%20record%20956%20cases%2C%20the%20time%20period%20between%202010%20and%202020%20saw%20just%2071.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstitution%20benches%20comprise%20at%20least%20five%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20and%20are%20formed%20to%20adjudicate%20cases%20involving%20significant%20questions%20of%20law%20and%20interpretations%20of%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20law%20minister%20Ar