20a%20potent%20expression%20of%20the%20tribes%E2%80%99%20determination%20to%20reclaim%20their%20rights%20and%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeel%20back%20the%20layers%20of%20Northeast%20India%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20politics%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F07e0c189-0f68-4c73-b31c-d982915cfa0c%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1691213401000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw1xInElmyvwNwKJGjyMzY4P%5C%22%3Erich%20tapestry%20of%20diverse%20cultures%2C%20traditions%2C%20and%20struggles%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20unveiled.%20The%20clash%20between%20traditional%20tribal%20governance%20and%20the%20modern%20state%20has%20ignited%20conflicts%20and%20sowed%20aspirations%20for%20autonomy%20and%20self-rule.%20In%20the%20quest%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20society%2C%20striking%20a%20balance%20between%20preserving%20indigenous%20traditions%20and%20accommodating%20the%20aspirations%20of%20tribal%20communities%20remains%20a%20paramount%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20of%20field-based%20reports%20spotlighting%20lesser-known%20cross-cutting%20humanitarian%20issues%20that%20are%20emanating%20from%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%20In%20addition%20to%20understanding%20the%20socio-economic%20impact%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20series%20also%20seeks%20to%20map%20out%20instances%20of%20resilience%2C%20local%20innovations%20in%20humanitarian%20action%2C%20and%20examples%20of%20community%20peacebuilding%20in%20the%20context.%20This%20series%20is%20being%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%20in%20close%20collaboration%20with%20field%20collaborators%2C%20social%20organizations%20and%20civil%20society%20partners%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20Northeast.%20Deepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Amisha%20Singh%2C%20Samragnee%20Chakroborty%2C%20Shalaka%20Adhikari%20and%20Aditi%20Desai%20are%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690626639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-tribal-politics-behind-manipur-conflict%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20particularly%20until%20the%20CAA-NRC%20issue%20riled%20up%20states%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20ethnic%20tensions%20were%20beginning%20to%20subside%20while%20communities%20were%20collaboratively%20progressing%20towards%20realising%20better%20developmental%20opportunities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-tribal-politics-behind-manipur-conflict%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Declare%20MHADEI%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20as%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%203%20Months%2C%20Bombay%20HC%20Orders%20Goa%20Govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F28200004%2FImage_1_by_Sudhir_Mishra-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20judgment%20last%20week%2C%20Bombay%20high%20court%20Justices%20M.S.%20Sonak%20and%20Bharat%20Deshpande%20directed%20the%20Goa%20government%20to%20declare%20MHADEI%20wildlife%20sanctuary%20in%20Goa%20as%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20within%20three%20months.%20While%20striking%20down%20the%20BJP-led%20Goa%20government%E2%80%99s%20plea%20to%20postpone%20the%20matter%2C%20Justices%20Sonak%20and%20Deshpande%20set%20the%20matter%20straight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20universe%2C%20man%20and%20animals%20are%20equally%20placed%2C%20but%20human%20rights%20approach%20to%20environmental%20protection%20in%20case%20of%20conflict%2C%20is%20often%20based%20on%20anthropocentricity.%20Man-animal%20conflict%20often%20results%20not%20because%20animals%20encroach%20human%20territories%20but%20vice%20versa%E2%80%A6This%20Court%20cannot%20blink%20at%20the%20reality%20that%20often%20at%20the%20State%20level%2C%20regional%2C%20parochial%2C%20anthropomorphic%2C%20and%20times%2C%20even%20narrow%20political%20considerations%20would%20prevail%20over%20the%20more%20significant%20national%20interests%20involved%20in%20conserving%20and%20protecting%20the%20tiger%20and%20the%20tiger%20habitat%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20Sonak%20and%20Deshpande%20observed%2C%20in%20what%20may%20be%20the%20most%20striking%20comment%20in%20recent%20times%20in%20the%20development%20versus%20conservation%20debate%20across%20the%20globe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20plea%20to%20convert%20the%20MHADEI%20wildlife%20sanctuary%20into%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20was%20moved%20by%20the%20Goa%20Foundation%2C%20a%20non-profit%20environment%20rights%20advocacy%20organisation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flawbeat.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fbombay-high-court-orders-goa-government-declare-mhadei-wildlife-sanctuary-tiger%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ELawbeat%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20union%20government%20and%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20since%202011%20had%20been%20making%20several%20requests%20to%20the%20Goa%20government%20to%20notify%20the%20Mhadei%20wildlife%20sanctuary%20and%20some%20contiguous%20forest%20areas%20as%20tiger%20reserve.%20But%20the%20Goa%20government%20remained%20opposed%20to%20it%2C%20citing%20conflicting%20interests%20between%20forest%20dwellers%20and%20advocates%20of%20conservation.%20However%2C%20conservation%20experts%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20declaration%20of%20the%20wildlife%20sanctuary%20into%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20may%20restrict%20the%20Goa%20government%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20open%20up%20forest%20resources%20for%20commercial%20use.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20matter%20came%20to%20a%20head%20when%20in%20January%202020%20a%20tigress%20and%20three%20cubs%20died%20due%20to%20some%20poisoning%20in%20the%20sanctuary.%20The%20Goa%20Foundation%2C%20citing%20government%20inaction%2C%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20thereafter.%20The%20matter%20was%20being%20heard%20at%20the%20Goa%20Bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20since%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20directing%20the%20Goa%20government%20to%20declare%20the%20sanctuary%20as%20a%20tiger%20reserve%2C%20the%20bench%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tiger%20is%20a%20unique%20animal%20which%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20health%20and%20diversity%20of%20an%20ecosystem.%20It%20is%20a%20top%20predator%20at%20the%20apex%20of%20the%20food%20chain.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20tigers%20in%20the%20forest%20is%20an%20indicator%20of%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20ecosystem.%20Protection%20of%20tigers%20in%20forests%20protects%20the%20habitats%20of%20several%20other%20species.%20Indirect%20benefits%20of%20preserving%20a%20tiger%20include%20several%20ecosystem%20services%20like%20protection%20of%20rivers%20and%20other%20water%20sources%2C%20prevention%20of%20soil%20erosion%20and%20improvement%20of%20ecological%20services%20like%20pollination%2C%20water%20table%20retention%2C%20etc.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20this%20top%20predator%20indicates%20that%20its%20ecosystem%20is%20not%20sufficiently%20protected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Goa%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20cited%20many%20references%20in%20which%20the%20Goa%20government%20refused%20to%20respond%20to%20repeated%20requests%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%2C%20alleging%20inaction%20and%20failure%20to%20stick%20to%20its%20statutory%20duty%20on%20its%20part.%20The%20Goa%20government%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20claimed%20that%20it%20had%20at%20no%20point%20refused%20to%20send%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20about%20converting%20the%20sanctuary%20into%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20or%20notify%20is%20as%20one%20but%20added%20that%20the%20time%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20right%20for%20sanctuary%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20as%20some%20issues%20regarding%20forest%20dwellers%20needed%20to%20be%20settled%20first.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Goa%20government%20cited%20the%20recommendations%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20state%20board%20for%20wildlife%20which%20had%20recently%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20setting%20up%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20in%20the%20MHADEI%20wildlife%20sanctuary%2C%20arguing%20that%20such%20a%20decision%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cpremature%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20feasible%E2%80%9D.%20Even%20the%20chief%20minister%20Pramod%20Sawant%20said%20that%20the%20Wildlife%20Act%20and%20the%20NTCA%E2%80%99s%20guidelines%20were%20not%20fit%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20a%20small%20state%20like%20Goa.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20repeated%20delays%20in%20responding%20to%20central%20notices%20and%20unclear%20positions%20led%20the%20high%20court%20to%20rule%20against%20the%20Goa%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EState%E2%80%99s%20forest%20minister%20Vishwajit%20Rane%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20will%20move%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20vacate%20the%20order.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20examining%20the%20HC%20order%2C%20we%20shall%20explore%20all%20options%20before%20approaching%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20have%20this%20order%20vacated.%20We%20respect%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20HC%2C%20but%20as%20a%20State%20Government%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20by%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20State%20Wildlife%20Board%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rane%20tweeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690626103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F28200004%2FImage_1_by_Sudhir_Mishra-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdeclare-mhadei-wildlife-sanctuary-as-tiger-reserve-in-3-months-bombay-hc-tells-goa-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20Union%20government's%20orders%2C%20the%20Goa%20government%20has%20remained%20opposed%20to%20it%2C%20citing%20conflicting%20interests%20between%20forest%20dwellers%20and%20advocates%20of%20conservation.%20Conservation%20experts%20allege%20that%20the%20move%20may%20restrict%20the%20Goa%20government%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20open%20up%20forest%20resources%20for%20commercial%20use.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdeclare-mhadei-wildlife-sanctuary-as-tiger-reserve-in-3-months-bombay-hc-tells-goa-govt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20VP%20Harris%20embraces%20new%20attack%20role%2C%20draws%20fresh%20Republican%20fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690625806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102231431%2Cimgsize-848154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-vp-harris-embraces-new-attack-role-draws-fresh-republican-fire%2Farticleshow%2F102231370.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102231370.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20has%20shown%20a%20punchy%20side%20during%20a%20tour%20of%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20US%20states%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20attacking%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20for%20backing%20%26quot%3Brevisionist%20history%26quot%3B%20about%20slavery%2C%20telling%20Iowa%20he