6%2F362089181_783980739877403_4227865788093944571_n-2-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665665%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERavish%20Kumar%2C%20Vinay%20Shukla%20and%20John%20Oliver.%20Photo%3A%20Instagram%2F%40whilewewatched%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20shows%20became%20sold%20out%2C%20more%20shows%20were%20quickly%20added%2C%20often%20followed%20by%20conversations%20with%20the%20subject%20and%20the%20director%2C%20which%20felt%20both%20unusual%20and%20yet%20somehow%20right.%20The%20film%20has%20undoubtedly%20created%20a%20furore%20in%20NYC%20and%20before%20that%20in%20London.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F20%2Fmovies%2Fwhile-we-watched-review.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rightly%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwake%20up%20call%20for%20India%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffilm%2F2023%2Fjul%2F16%2Fwhile-we-watched-review-ravish-kumar-nerve-shredding-life-as-a-journalist-in-india-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGuardian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20described%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etense%2C%20essential%20film-making%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20all%20this%20attention%20and%20the%20film%20being%20released%20first%20in%20September%202022%2C%20Shukla%20has%20repeatedly%20mentioned%20that%20he%20has%20not%20yet%20had%20a%20single%20offer%20to%20distribute%20the%20film%20in%20India.%20And%20while%20global%20viewership%20is%20crucial%20to%20let%20people%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20India%2C%20it%20is%20precisely%20in%20India%20that%20the%20film%20must%20be%20seen%20to%20understand%20the%20current%20state%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98largest%20democracy%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20experience%20of%20one%20of%20its%20most%20popular%20TV%20anchors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20part%20of%20the%20film%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20NDTV%20newsroom%20where%20Kumar%20worked%20on%20his%20daily%20Hindi%20language%20show%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Time%20with%20Ravish%20Kumar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20camera%20followed%20him%20closely%20while%20he%20bounced%20off%20daily%20news%20ideas%20with%20his%20colleagues%2C%20drafted%20his%20evening%20read%20out%2C%20reacted%20to%20dramatic%20news%20as%20they%20unfolded%2C%20and%20listened%20patiently%20to%20his%20team%20members%20as%20they%20pondered%20over%20their%20career%20options%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20changing%20media%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20emerges%20from%20those%20newsroom%20shots%20is%20a%20beleaguered%20Ravish%20Kumar%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20explain%20to%20his%20audience%20the%20onslaught%20on%20democracy%20unleashed%20by%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20government%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIssues%20ranged%20from%20jingoism%20and%20war-mongering%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20targeting%20and%20lynching%20of%20Muslim%20youth%2C%20incarceration%20of%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20professors%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20students%2C%20and%20silencing%20of%20newspapers%20and%20journalists%20who%20dared%20to%20question%20the%20government%20policies.%20It%20was%20gradually%20a%20bare-bones%20newsroom%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20Ravish%20Kumar%20that%20was%20responding%20to%20these%20unparalleled%20daily%20developments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20film%20does%20brilliantly%20is%20to%20situate%20Kumar%2C%20his%20prime-time%20show%2C%20and%20NDTV%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20media%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20particularly%20television%20news%20%E2%80%93%20that%20was%20openly%20spewing%20hatred%2C%20spreading%20misinformation%2C%20and%20goading%20crowds%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28171909%2FF8336CC7-9A67-4E0B-A372-FF8D82E22C16.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28171909%2FF8336CC7-9A67-4E0B-A372-FF8D82E22C16.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28171909%2FF8336CC7-9A67-4E0B-A372-FF8D82E22C16-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665668%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%20screening%20in%20New%20York.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMultiple%20media%20channels%2C%20both%20Hindi%20and%20English%2C%20indulged%20in%20defining%20an%20exclusionary%20meaning%20of%20patriotism%20and%20delivered%20their%20unadulterated%20hate%20messages%20to%20millions%20of%20homes%20every%20day.%20Kumar%20completely%20rejected%20the%20dominant%20format%20of%20other%20prime-time%20anchors%20that%20relied%20on%20sensational%20and%20high-decibel%20debate%20among%20talking%20heads%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20distribute%20hatred%20as%20news.%20The%20show%20became%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20create%20an%20alternative%20explanation%20of%20what%20was%20unfolding%20every%20day%20and%20done%20through%20his%20sheer%20power%20of%20storytelling%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20long%20monologues%20that%20tried%20to%20break%20through%20the%20fog.%20Being%20a%20very%20popular%20anchor%20on%20NDTV%20for%20multiple%20years%2C%20people%20flocked%20to%20his%20show%20to%20hear%20his%20views%20on%20the%20pressing%20issues%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShukla%20has%20mentioned%20in%20interviews%20that%20he%20liked%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20persuasive%20storytelling%20alongside%20his%20connection%20with%20the%20audience%20that%20allowed%20the%20anchor%20to%20often%20even%20chide%20them%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cjr.org%2Fthe_media_today%2Fqa_while_we_watched_documentary_india.php%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewatching%20other%20channels%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20name%20of%20news.%20But%20really%20what%20he%20ends%20up%20doing%20is%20to%20tell%20us%20a%20larger%20story%20of%20attempted%20decimation%3A%20of%20the%20news%20network%20that%20Kumar%20was%20a%20part%20of-NDTV%2C%20of%20the%20reporters%2C%20support%20staff%2C%20distribution%2C%20viewership%2C%20and%20above%20all%20what%20hurt%20Kumar%20the%20most-%20his%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20giving%20away%20too%20much%20from%20the%20film%2C%20one%20can%20only%20note%20the%20poignant%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20film%20captures%20this%20gradual%20decline%20in%20the%20media%20network%20and%20Ravish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20own%20show%20then%20slowly%20creeping%20into%20his%20life%20as%20his%20family%20starts%20feeling%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20hostility%20and%20trolling%20around%20them.%20The%20film%20offers%20you%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20your%20phone%20number%20is%20circulated%20in%20the%20media%20and%20you%20dare%20to%20listen%20and%20occasionally%20respond%20to%20those%20who%20abuse%20you%20with%20death%20threats%20merely%20makes%20one%20both%20horrified%20and%20truly%20terrified.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20Kumar%20often%20speaks%20back%20with%20patience%2C%20laughs%2C%20and%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20sings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20incredulous%20moment%20that%20just%20tells%20you%20something%20about%20his%20faith%20that%20if%20only%20he%20could%20communicate%20with%20his%20audience%20more%2C%20he%20can%20maybe%20make%20a%20difference.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.v-dem.net%2Fdocuments%2F12%2Fdr_2021.pdf%5C%22%3EVarieties%20of%20Democracy%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20dataset%20from%20202%20countries%20on%20measuring%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20noted%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20share%20of%20the%20population%20under%20autocracies%20increased%20from%2048%25%20in%202010%20to%2068%25%20in%202020.%20India%20is%20among%20the%20top%2010%20on%20this%20list.%20The%20report%20noted%20that%20the%20largest%20democracy%20is%20now%20an%20%E2%80%9Celectoral%20autocracy%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20continued%20decline%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fv-dem.net%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2023%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20far%20as%20media%20freedom%20is%20concerned%2C%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20(RSF)%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsf.org%2Fen%2Findex%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0noted%20that%20India%20has%20declined%20from%20150%20to%20161%20in%20their%20world%20ranking%20and%20journalists%20continued%20to%20be%20detained%20and%20censored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalist%20Siddique%20Kappan%20spent%20more%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-64494426%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etwo%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20jail%20for%20daring%20to%20report%20on%20the%20gangrape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20Dalit%20woman%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Hathras.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20rankings%20reflect%20general%20trends%20and%20there%20can%20be%20debates%20on%20the%20actual%20terminology%20of%20electoral%20autocracy%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20translates%20what%20these%20figures%20mean%20in%20the%20everyday%20Indian%20experience%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20lack%20of%20press%20freedom%20and%20rights%20in%20general.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20know%20how%20Ravish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20stint%20at%20NDTV%20ended%20%E2%80%93%20the%20film%20does%20not%20show%20that.%20But%20it%20shows%20%E2%80%93%20through%20different%20moments%20in%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20some%20very%20tender%20and%20some%20harsh%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20fall%20in%20line%20and%20compromise%20even%20as%20the%20resources%20at%20his%20disposal%20were%20depleting%20fast%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20literally%20collapsing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20film%20also%20depicts%20how%20Kumar%20starts%20realising%20that%20a%20section%20of%20the%20audience%20that%20doted%20on%20him%20was%20slowly%20getting%20persuaded%20by%20the%20frenzy%20and%20the%20hatred%20espoused%20by%20other%20channels%20and%20the%20world%20around%20him.%20The%20film%20beautifully%20captures%20a%20deeply%20complex%20Kumar%20who%20acknowledges%20the%20changes%20that%20Indian%20society%20and%20politics%20is%20undergoing%20but%20also%20exudes%20an%20unfaltering%20faith%20in%20his%20ability%20to%20level%20with%20his%20audience.%20That%20is%20Ravish%20Kumar%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20his%20calling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJinee%20Lokaneeta%20and%20Sangay%20Mishra%20teach%20Political%20Science%20at%20Drew%20University%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690624817000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28172559%2F359665950_1676607739434024_4017294775728816439_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-while-we-watched-ravish-kumar-is-a-picture-of-courage-in-perilous-times%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20global%20attention%20t