E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20and%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20leader%20Zoramthanga%20said%20his%20party%20will%20leave%20the%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20if%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20(UCC)%20was%20imposed%20on%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20this%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-conflict-a-concern-needs-a-political-solution-says-mizoram-cm-101690570852864.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Saturday%2C%20July%2029%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20being%20%5Ba%5D%20member%20of%20the%20NDA%20is%20concerned%2C%20my%20party%20is%20among%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20NDA.%20But%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20we%20will%20follow%20every%20policy.%20When%20%5Ban%5D%20issue%20comes%20against%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Mizo%20people%2C%20my%20party%20will%20totally%20object%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zoramthanga%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20and%20my%20party%20totally%20reject%20%5Bthe%5D%20UCC%20%E2%80%A6%20if%20%5Bthe%5D%20UCC%20is%20going%20to%20be%20imposed%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20we%20cannot%20be%20part%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20NDA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20secessionist%20fighter%20clarified%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20Union%20government%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20let%20matters%20reach%20that%20breaking%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20the%20NDA%20will%20in%20the%20way%20that%20is%20%5Bsic%5D%20wise%20enough%2C%20mature%20enough%20and%20see%20that%20a%20thing%20like%20UCC%20does%20not%20help%20them.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20they%20%5Bwill%5D%20make%20any%20issue%20which%20will%20necessitate%20the%20MNF%20leaving%20the%20NDA%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UCC%20is%20a%20proposed%20single%20set%20of%20laws%20that%20would%20uniformly%20govern%20personal%20matters%2C%20including%20marriage%2C%20divorce%20and%20inheritance%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20different%20religious%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmizoram%2Fucc-against-ethnic-minorities-interest-mizoram-cm-8749891%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20has%20opposed%20a%20UCC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20would%20conflict%20with%20the%20Mizos%E2%80%99%20constitutionally%20protected%20customary%20laws%2C%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20which%20leads%20the%20NDA%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-files-affidavit-on-uniform-civil-code-in-sc-says-different-religions-following-different-laws-affronting-national-unity%2Farticle66026485.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esupports%20a%20UCC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20has%20consistently%20promised%20to%20implement%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98I%20do%20not%20interfere%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20internal%20affairs%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20interview%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20addressed%20accusations%20against%20Zoramthanga%20that%20he%20was%20interfering%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20Manipur%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcbi-to-take-over-manipur-sexual-assault-case-say-officials%2Farticle67127960.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econtinues%20to%20be%20affected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20deadly%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20state%E2%80%99s%20Mizo%20community%20bears%20close%20ethnic%20ties%20to%20the%20Chin%20people%20of%20Myanmar%20and%20the%20Kuki%20people%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latter%20are%20one%20of%20the%20two%20warring%20factions%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20with%20the%20other%20being%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20Meitei%20ethnic%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20a%20video%20surfaced%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eearlier%20this%20month%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob%20allegedly%20comprising%20Meitei%20men%2C%20Zoramthanga%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmizoram-cm-joins-solidarity-march-for-kuki-zo-people-in-manipur%2Farticle67120367.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eparticipated%20in%20a%20solidarity%20march%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kuki%20community%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2026.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20wound%20is%20deep%20and%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20heal%20this%20with%20a%20pain-killer.%20It%20needs%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fjul%2F26%2Fcm-biren-asks-mizoram-counterpart-zoramthanga-not-to-meddle-in-manipurs-internal-matters-2598845.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ethnic%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march.jpeg%201152w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665774%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZoramthanga%20at%20the%20solidarity%20march%20in%20Aizawl%20on%20July%2026.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40ITFLMedia_Cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20in%20Manipur%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fdissent-against-mizoram-cm-zoramthanga-mounts-effigies-burned%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresponded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20burning%20effigies%20of%20Zoramthanga%20in%20Imphal%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20capital%20city%2C%20and%20chief%20minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20asked%20his%20Mizoram%20counterpart%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20%E2%80%A6%20internal%20affairs%20of%20other%20%5Bstates%5D%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-government-not-against-kuki-community-but-illegal-immigrants-cm-biren%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20response%20to%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20that%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20of%20the%20trouble%20in%20Manipur%2C%20thousands%20of%20%E2%80%A6%20Kuki%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20(IDPs)%20have%20come%20to%20Mizoram.%20Whether%20it%20is%20forced%20upon%20me%20or%20not%2C%20we%20have%20to%20act%20and%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20it%20as%20it%20affects%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%2012%2C000%20Kuki%20people%20displaced%20by%20the%20violence%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcant-manage-refugees-polls-alone-humanitarian-crisis-looms-mizoram-cms-sos-in-letter-to-modi%2F1688143%2F%3Famp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esought%20refuge%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20alleged%20that%20the%20union%20home%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20help%20to%20his%20administration%20in%20handling%20the%20influx%20of%20Kuki%20refugees%20into%20his%20state%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20enough%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20accepting%20Chin%20refugees%20fleeing%20the%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20ethnically-related%20people%20leaving%20Bangladesh%20for%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar%20are%20concerned%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20are%20not%20signatory%20to%20UN%20Refugees.%20I%20told%20my%20chief%20secretary%20that%20we%20are%20merely%20following%20what%20%E2%80%A6%20India%20had%20done%20in%201970%20and%201971%20when%20millions%20of%20East%20Pakistan%20refugees%20had%20crossed%20over%20to%20India%20and%20%5Bwere%5D%20looked%20after%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20East%20Pakistan%20people%20were%20given%20that%20support%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20give%20it%20to%20people%20from%20Burma%2FMyanmar%3F%20The%20same%20formula%20has%20to%20be%20applied.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98No%20anger%20against%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20while%20he%20was%20surprised%20by%20what%20he%20said%20were%20inadequate%20efforts%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20helping%20the%20refugees%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20remain%20a%20partner%20within%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20anger%20against%20the%20NDA%3B%20it%20has%20been%20constituted%20by%20a%20number%20of%20political%20parties%20to%20form%20an%20alliance.%20With%20the%20present%20Union%20government%2C%20I%20am%20a%20little%20surprised%20by%20their%20attitude%20in%20dealing%20with%20Manipur%20and%20not%20giving%20help%20to%20the%20refugees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20I%20requested%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20to%20look%20into%20the%20refugee%20and%20IDPs%E2%80%99%20crises%20from%20a%20different%20angle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20what%20it%20would%20take%20to%20end%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20Zoramthanga%20said%20the%20following%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20solution%20is%2C%20let%20the%20Manipur%20and%20the%20central%20governments%20come%20together%20and%20consult%20the%20concerned%20people%20(Kuki%20and%20the%20Meitei%20people)%20and%20let%20the%20Union%20government%20settle%20this%20politically.%20That%20is%20the%20only%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690623028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F20142741%2FZoramthanga.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fzoramthanga-on-ucc-and-manipur-violence%22%2C%22summar