A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F06182509%2F2022_4img06_Apr_2022_PTI04_06_2022_000101B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartisan-politics-more-important-jaishankar-slams-opposition-over-parliament-disruption%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20MPs%20in%20Parliament%20protested%20vociferously%20demanding%20answers%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%20Disrupted%20in%20parliament%2C%20Jaishankar%20released%20a%20video%20statement%20on%20Twitter%20on%20foreign%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartisan-politics-more-important-jaishankar-slams-opposition-over-parliament-disruption%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Disquiet%20in%20Opposition%20Ranks%20as%20Sharad%20Pawar%20Set%20to%20Share%20Stage%20with%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F11113000%2FSharad-Pawar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20An%20upcoming%20event%20in%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20are%20likely%20to%20share%20the%20stage%20has%20set%20off%20a%20sense%20of%20disquiet%20among%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20opposition.%20Pawar%20has%20been%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20rebellion%20in%20his%20party%20ranks%2C%20with%20its%20top%20leadership%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20Dilip%20Walse-Patil%2C%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20and%20Chagan%20Bhujbal%20along%20with%20several%20NCP%20legislators%20recently%20joining%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-BJP%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20Pawar%20in%20his%20statements%2C%20social%20media%20messaging%2C%20and%20posturing%20in%20the%20ongoing%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%20has%20been%20unequivocal%20about%20his%20loyalty%20to%20the%20recently%20formed%20opposition%20front%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%2C%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(I.N.D.I.A)%2C%20he%20has%20also%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakaway-faction-of-ncp-calls-on-sharad-pawar-in-an-impromptu-meet-for-the-second-day-in-a-row%5C%22%3Eclosed-door%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20party%20rebels%20at%20least%20thrice%20over%20the%20last%20month%2C%20apparently%20to%20keep%20his%20flock%20intact.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20emerging%20from%20Maharashtra%20have%20indicated%20that%20Pawar%2C%20true%20to%20his%20wily%20personality%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20made%20his%20political%20stance%20as%20clear%20as%20he%20should%20have%2C%20and%20that%20his%20efforts%20to%20keep%20his%20party%20united%20may%20also%20lead%20him%20to%20switch%20towards%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20such%20circumstances%2C%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20share%20the%20stage%20with%20Modi%20has%20had%20the%20rumour%20mills%20working%20overtime%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%20creating%20greater%20confusion%20among%20opposition%20ranks.%20The%20event%20on%20August%201%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Smarak%20Mandir%20Trust%20to%20confer%20an%20award%20to%20Modi%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Cleadership%20and%20efforts%20to%20instill%20a%20sense%20of%20patriotism%20among%20citizens%E2%80%9D.%20Pawar%20has%20been%20invited%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20of%20the%20ceremony%20in%20which%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20are%20also%20among%20the%20VIP%20invitees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20two%20factions%20in%20the%20NCP%20spoke%20critically%20of%20each%20other%20in%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20rebellion%2C%20both%20sides%20restrained%20themselves%20from%20attacking%20each%20other%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Praful%20Patel%20met%20the%20NCP%20supremo%20at%20his%20house%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdisquiet-in-opposition-over-sharad-pawar-sharing-stage-with-modi-on-august-1%2Farticle67132012.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20parties%20on%20Friday%2C%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20joining%20the%20event%20organised%20to%20award%20Modi.%20They%20believed%20that%20it%20would%20create%20bad%20%E2%80%9Coptics%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20coalition%20at%20a%20time%20when%20they%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20stiff%20battle%20with%20the%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20and%20have%20moved%20a%20no-trust%20motion%20against%20the%20union%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20regional%20party%2C%20the%20daily%20reported%2C%20was%20the%20first%20party%20to%20express%20its%20disquiet%20over%20the%20development%2C%20while%20other%20leaders%20urged%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20to%20dissuade%20Pawar%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENCP%E2%80%98s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Vandana%20Chavan%20was%20the%20only%20representative%20from%20the%20party%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20who%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20issue.%20It%20is%20learnt%20that%20a%20top%20leader%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20awaken%20those%20who%20are%20sleeping%20but%20can%20we%20awaken%20those%20who%20are%20pretending%20to%20sleep%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20INDIA%20constituents%20were%20also%20worried%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20some%20o