0an%20educator.%20So%2C%20Garhwal%20English%20Medium%20School%20is%20the%20amalgamation%20of%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2065-year-old%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELori%20first%20visited%20India%20in%201998%20for%20a%20school%20field%20trip.%20During%20her%20time%20in%20the%20country%2C%20she%20was%20concerned%20about%20children%20living%20on%20the%20streets.%20She%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20So%2C%20a%20year%20later%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20volunteered%20at%20several%20NGOs.%20She%20travelled%20back%20to%20India%20every%20summer%20for%20four%20years%20to%20do%20the%20same%20before%20starting%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20Lori%20returned%20to%20India%20to%20pursue%20PhD%20in%20Landour%20Language%20School.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20my%20thesis%20on%20language%20learning%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20villages%20and%20talk%20to%20people.%20I%20was%20a%20very%20hands-on%20researcher%20and%20wanted%20to%20have%20real%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20has%20volunteers%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-150x79.jpg%2015