red%20the%20cost%20of%20her%20gear%2C%20but%20she%20is%20now%20seeking%20sponsors%20for%20her%20upcoming%20expeditions.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20sponsor%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20them%20at%20harshabennur%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690379662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-1690377858.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20trekked%20to%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%20in%202022%2C%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20eight-year-old%20Aadya%20Bennur%20has%20now%20scaled%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20with%20her%20father%20Harsha.%20She%20is%20one%20of%20the%20youngest%20mountaineers%20to%20summit%20the%20peak.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325197%2Fbengaluru-aadya-bennur-young-mountaineer-ebc-trek-mt-kilimanjaro-peak-father-shares-routine%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Planning%20a%20Vacation%20With%20Your%20Baby%3F%202%20Friends%20Are%20Taking%20Moms%20%26%20Kids%20to%20Trips%20Across%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMotherhood%20is%20a%20fulfilling%20yet%20challenging%20journey%20that%20often%20brings%20doubts%20to%20our%20minds.%20%E2%80%98Will%20we%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20doing%20the%20things%20we%20love%20as%20we%20did%20before%3F%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20common%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20new%20mother%2C%20I%20know%20I%20have%20these%20doubts.%20And%20I%20felt%20most%20comforted%20when%20I%20spoke%20to%20other%20mothers%20who%20shared%20similar%20experiences.%20If%20a%20simple%20coffee%20with%20a%20friend%20going%20through%20the%20same%20phase%20felt%20relaxing%2C%20imagine%20how%20wonderful%20it%20would%20be%20to%20go%20on%20a%20trip%20together%2C%20just%20mothers%20and%20their%20kids!%