%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406.jpg%201088w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325206%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20has%20planned%2020%20trips%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20tweaks%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20manageable%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20to%20places%20which%20aren%E2%80%99t%20considered%20%E2%80%98kid-friendly%E2%80%99%20like%20Reunion%20Island%2C%20Morocco%20and%20Egypt.%20My%20daughter%20enjoyed%20it.%20Kids%20will%20always%20find%20a%20way%20to%20entertain%20themselves.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20always%20go%20to%20zoos%20or%20parks.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20the%20sensory%20experience%20of%20being%20in%20a%20new%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20I%20travelled%20solo%2C%20then%20with%20my%20husband%20whose%20interests%20are%20very%20different.%20Now%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20interests%20are%20different.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20needs%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20manage%20their%20interests%20themselves.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it%20for%20them.%20But%20in%20this%20process%