ch%20them%20young%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20one%20of%20their%20programmes%20says.%20This%20inclusion%20centres%20around%20their%20education%2C%20but%20also%20looks%20to%20integrate%20them%20into%20the%20mainstream%20as%20a%20whole%20and%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Maria%20Montessori%20began%20her%20work%2C%20it%20was%20for%20disabled%20children.%20But%20parents%20soon%20realised%20that%20this%20could%20work%20for%20other%20children%20too.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20always%20telling%20people%2C%20that%20when%20you%20target%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20child%20in%20the%20room%2C%20your%20whole%20classroom%20will%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Everybody%20is%20welcome%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatika%E2%80%99s%20work%20with%20disabled%20children%20began%20when%20Jo%20and%20her%20husband%20Ravi%20adopted%20Moy%20Moy%2C%20who%20also%20lived%20with%20a%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20as%20just%20an%20inclusive%20play%20centre%20where%20children%20of%20all%20kinds%20could%20come%20after%20school%20and%20engage%20in%20fun%20activities.%20The%20only%20rules%20were%20that%20you%20play%20fair%20and%20welcome%20everybody%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20lots%20of%20kids%20with%20disabilities%20coming%20in%20naturally%3B%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20active%20effort%20on%20our%20part%2C%20but%20they%20came%20because%20of%20the%20inclusive%20environment%20we%E2%80%99d%20built.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FClDz_IEOdMY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FClDz