0as%20if%20they%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20her%20difficulties.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20this%20school%20system%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20right%20for%20Moy%20Moy.%20Everything%20at%20the%20Foundation%20has%20evolved%20from%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20put%20in%20place%20many%20provisions%20in%20the%20form%20of%20laws%20and%20policies%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20the%20implementation%20remains%20questionable.%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20of%20all%20the%20children%20with%20disabilities%20in%20India%2C%20three-fourths%20of%20those%20aged%20aged%20five%20don%E2%80%99t%20attend%20any%20educational%20institution.%20About%2012%25%20drop%20out%2C%20and%2027%25%20have%20never%20attended%20any%20educational%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20UNICEF%20report%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20early%20years%20(0%20to%208%20years)%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime.%20The%20foundations%20of%20all%20learning%20are%20laid%20during%20these%20years.%20Getting%20the%20foundations%20right%20carries%20huge%20future%20benefits%3A%20better%20learning%20in%20school%20and%20higher%20educational%20attainment%2C%20which%20results%20in%20major%20social%20and%20economic%20gains%20for%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22inclusive%20education%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%20820w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-500x282.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-768x433.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUNICEF%20reports%20that%20the%20early%20years%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime%3B%20Photo%3A%20Representational%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F234151%2Fnew-education-policy-2020-pdf-hrd-ministry-play-school-classes-vocational-coding-bagless-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Education%20Policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20laid%20great%20emphasis%20on%20inclusion%20in%20education%20that%20takes%20into%20consideration%20local%20contexts%20and%20diversity.%20The%20framework%20asserts%20that%20quality%20in%20the%20early%20childhood%20care%20ecosystem%20(ECCE)%20is%20the%20highest%20priority%2C%20as%20is%20the%20inclusion%20and%20equal%20participation%20of%20children%20with%20disabilities%20and%20those%20from%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20we%20extend%20the%20same%20future%20benefits%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%20who%20are%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20an%20already%20fractured%20educational%20system%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20first%20programmes%20that%20the%20Foundation%20started%20was%20Karuna%20Vihar%2C%20an%20early%20childhood%20intervention%20centre%20that%20encourages%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%200%20and%206%20by%20building%20on%20their%20strengths.%20Parents%20or%20guardians