ng%20used%20by%20chefs%20who%20cook%20for%20dogs.%20Chennai-based%20Sneha%20Sridhar%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdog%20chef%E2%80%9D%2C%20got%20a%20spitz%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20was%20looking%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270443%2Fchuk-biodegradable-compostable-waste-sugarcane-fibre-tableware%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20tableware%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1-1690203391.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20says%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20products%20makes%20them%20safe%20to%20be%20consumed%20by%20animals.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1-1690203391.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1-1690203391-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1-1690203391-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1-1690203391-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1-1690203391-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324930%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Rishabh%20says%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20products%20makes%20them%20safe%20to%20be%20consumed%20by%20animals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDogs%20might%20bite%20into%20the%20paper%20tableware%20and%20quickly%20swallow%20them.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20edible%20plates%20cause%20no%20harm%20even%20if%20my%20dog%20consumes%20them%20as%20it%20is%20made%20of%20just