n-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FKahi-Debe-Sandesh-1689943464-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FKahi-Debe-Sandesh-1689943464-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FKahi-Debe-Sandesh-1689943464-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FKahi-Debe-Sandesh-1689943464-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FKahi-Debe-Sandesh-1689943464-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324749%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20Kahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20(1965)%20directed%20by%20Manu%20Nayak%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20A%20photobook%20by%20Aayush%20Chandrawanshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20films%20that%20set%20the%20precedent%20for%20these%20movies%20was%20the%20seemingly%20obscure%20production%20%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20Chhattisgarhi%20film%20released%20in%201965%2C%20which%20became%20among%20the%20first%20in%20India%20to%20openly%20discuss%20evils%20like%20untouchability%20and%20caste%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202018%20interview%20with%20filmmaker%20and%20documentary%20photographer%20Aayush%20Chandrawanshi%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20film%20Many%20Nayak%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20determined%20to%20make%20a%20film%20in%20the%20Chhattisgarhi%20dialect%20and%20to%20name%20it%3Cem%3E%20Kahi%20Debe%20Sandes%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20a%20theme%20in%20my%20mind%20which%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20childhood%20experiences.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20made%20Nayak%E2%80%99s%20film%20so%20remarkable%20was%20its%20willingness%20to%20take%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20inter-caste%20marriages%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20is%20still%20discouraged%20and%20frowned%20upon%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20it%20was%20among%20the%20first%20artistic%20pieces%20of%20work%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F168844%2Fias-hero-rajasthan-caste-discrimination-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20open%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20topics%20we%20still%20skirt%20around%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20film%20ahead%20of%20its%20time%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20the%20Indian%20film%20industry%20was%20dominated%20by%20Hindi-language%20movies%2C%20thus%20providing%20little%20to%20no%20opportunity%20for%20regional%20script%20movies.%20This%20spell%20ended%20in%201963%20with%20Kundan%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Bhojpuri%20film%20%3Cem%3EGanga%20Maiya%20Tohe%20Piyari%20Chadhaibo%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20poignant%20film%20on%20widow%20remarriage.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20young%20film%20enthusiast%20Manu%20Nayak%20was%20so%20influenced%20by%20this%20that%20it%20compelled%20him%20to%20make%20a%20Chhattisgarhi%20film%20on%20a%20subject%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Flawyer-dedicated-two-decades-to-helping-inter-caste-couples-love-freely-live-safely%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20was%20passionate%20about%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20353px)%20100vw%2C%20353px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-3-1689943324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20faced%20major%20backlash%20following%20its%20release%20for%20shedding%20light%20on%20caste%20discrimination%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-3-1689943324.jpg%20353w%2C%20htt